#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail;'s configuration window lets you configure &kmail;. You can reach it "
"via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Configure &kmail;...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"okno za konfiguracijo &kmail; vam omogoča, da konfigurirate &kmail;. Do "
"njega lahko pridete prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Konfiguriraj &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "The dialog has several buttons across the bottom."
msgstr "Pogovorno okno ima na dnu več gumbov."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: configure.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will open The &kmail; Handbook (this manual) at the appropriate page."
msgstr "To bo odprlo Priročnik &kmail; (ta priročnik) na ustrezni strani."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: configure.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset"
msgstr "Ponastavi"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This resets all the changes you have made since you last saved the settings."
msgstr ""
"S tem ponastavite vse spremembe, ki ste jih opravili od zadnjega "
"shranjevanja nastavitev."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: configure.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defaults"
msgstr "Privzeto"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will reset the configuration options on the current page to the default "
"values."
msgstr ""
"S tem bodo možnosti konfiguracije na trenutni strani ponastavljene na "
"privzete vrednosti."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: configure.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>OK</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>OK</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "This saves the settings and closes the configuration dialog."
msgstr "To shrani nastavitve in zapre pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: configure.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply"
msgstr "Uporabi"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "This saves the settings without closing the configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Tako shranite nastavitve, ne da bi zaprli pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: configure.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Prekliči"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This closes the configuration dialog without saving the changes you have "
"made."
msgstr ""
"S tem zaprete pogovorno okno konfiguracije, ne da bi shranili opravljene "
"spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configuration dialog is divided into six subsets, each of them "
"represented by one of the icons in the list on the left. These subsets are "
"described in detail below."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo je razdeljeno na šest podsklopov, od katerih "
"je vsak predstavljen z eno od ikon na seznamu na levi strani. Te podskupine "
"so podrobno opisane v nadaljevanju."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accounts Page"
msgstr "Stran z uporabniškimi računi"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> page is automatically presented when "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Configure &kmail;...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> is selected. There are four tabs: <guilabel>Identities</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Receiving</guilabel>, <guilabel>Sending</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>LDAP server</guilabel>. (The <guilabel>Identities</guilabel> tab "
"is illustrated in the <link linkend=\"configure-generalinfo\">Configure "
"&kmail;</link> section above.)"
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> se samodejno prikaže, ko je izbran "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Konfigururaj &kmail;...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Na voljo so štirje zavihki: <guilabel>Identitete</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Prejemanje</guilabel>, <guilabel>Pošiljanje</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Server LDAP</guilabel>. (Zavihek <guilabel>Identitete</guilabel> "
"je prikazan v zgornjem razdelku <link linkend=\"configure-generalinfo"
"\">Konfiguracija &kmail;</link>.)"

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Identities Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek identitete"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find a quick introduction to the <guilabel>Identities</guilabel> tab "
"in the <link linkend=\"getting-started\">Getting Started</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Hitro predstavitev zavihka <guilabel>Identitete</guilabel> najdete v "
"razdelku <link linkend=\"getting-started\">Začetek</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page allows you to create one or more <emphasis>Identities</emphasis>, "
"&ie;, combinations of a name, an email address, and some other settings. For "
"example, you can create one identity for business communication and another "
"for personal use. If you have more than one email address, you can create "
"one identity for each address. You will then be able to select a suitable "
"identity whenever you compose a new message."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani lahko ustvarite eno ali več <emphasis>Identitet</emphasis>, "
"&ie;, kombinacij imena, e-poštnega naslova in nekaterih drugih nastavitev. "
"Tako lahko na primer ustvarite eno identiteto za poslovno komunikacijo in "
"drugo za osebno uporabo. Če imate več e-poštnih naslovov, lahko za vsak "
"naslov ustvarite eno identiteto. Tako boste, ko boste ustvarili novo "
"sporočilo, lahko izbrali ustrezno identiteto."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog consists of a list of identities, plus buttons to manage them. "
"After initial setup, the list will always show at least one identity, which "
"is then the <guilabel>Default</guilabel> identity. To add a new identity to "
"the identity list, click on the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno je sestavljeno iz seznama identitet in gumbov za njihovo "
"upravljanje. Po začetni nastavitvi bo na seznamu vedno prikazana vsaj ena "
"identiteta, ki je nato <guilabel>Privzeta</guilabel> identiteta. Če želite "
"na seznam identitet dodati novo identiteto, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Dodaj..."
"</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The New Identity Dialog</title>"
msgstr "<title>Dialog za novo identiteto</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New Identity Dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dialog za novo identiteto</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New Identity Dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dialog za novo identiteto</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The New Identity Dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Dialog za novo identiteto</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a name for the new identity in the <guilabel>New Identity</guilabel> "
"edit field. This name will be shown in the identity list."
msgstr ""
"V urejevalno polje <guilabel>Nova identiteta</guilabel> vnesite ime za novo "
"identiteto. To ime bo prikazano na seznamu identitet."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose how the new identity is initialized by checking one of three "
"radio buttons."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko način inicializacije nove identitete tako, da izberete enega "
"od treh izbirnih gumbov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:177 configure.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "With empty fields"
msgstr "S praznimi polji"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All fields of the new identity will be cleared, or preset with standard "
"values."
msgstr ""
"Vsa polja nove identitete se izbrišejo ali pa se prednastavijo s "
"standardnimi vrednostmi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use System Settings values"
msgstr "Uporabi vrednosti nastavitev sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Uses the values from your default identity."
msgstr "Uporablja vrednosti iz privzete identitete."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duplicate existing identity"
msgstr "Podvoji obstoječo identiteto"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies all fields from an existing identity. You may choose which identity "
"to copy from by selecting the corresponding entry in the <guilabel>Existing "
"identities</guilabel> drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Kopira vsa polja iz obstoječe identitete. Identiteto, ki jo želite kopirati, "
"lahko izberete tako, da izberete ustrezen vnos v spustnem polju "
"<guilabel>Obstoječe identitete</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:205 configure.docbook:899 configure.docbook:1377
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošno</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Identity General</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Splošno za identitete</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Identity General</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Splošno za identitete</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Identity General</para>"
msgstr "<para>Splošno za identitete</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab allows you to specify some basic "
"settings for the currently selected identity."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>General</guilabel> omogoča določitev nekaterih osnovnih "
"nastavitev za trenutno izbrano identiteto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your name"
msgstr "Vaše ime"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter your full name here (sometimes also called <emphasis>display name</"
"emphasis>). Although this field is not mandatory, you should enter your name "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj vnesite svoje polno ime (včasih imenovano tudi <emphasis>prikazno ime</"
"emphasis>). Čeprav to polje ni obvezno, je zaželjeno, da vnesete svoje ime."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organization"
msgstr "Organizacija"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter your organization here. This field is optional."
msgstr "Vpišite vašo organizacijo. To polje ni obvezno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Email address</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>E-naslov</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter your email address here, &ie;, something like <userinput>joe@example."
"com</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj vnesite svoj e-poštni naslov, &ie;, na primer <userinput>joe@example."
"com</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Email address</title>"
msgstr "<title>E-naslov</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"So if your address is <replaceable>Joe User &lt;joe@example.com&gt;</"
"replaceable>, you should enter <userinput>Joe User</userinput> into the "
"<guilabel>Your name</guilabel> field and <userinput>joe@example.com</"
"userinput> into the <guilabel>Email address</guilabel> field."
msgstr ""
"Če je torej vaš naslov <replaceable>Joe User &lt;joe@example.com&gt;</"
"replaceable>, morate v polje <guilabel>Vaše ime</guilabel> vnesti "
"<userinput>Joe User</userinput>, v polje <guilabel>E-naslov</guilabel> pa "
"<userinput>joe@example.com</userinput>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Email aliases</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Psevdonimi pri e-naslovih</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This field contains alias addresses that also belong to this identity (as "
"opposed to representing a different identity). You may define multiple "
"aliases. To add another alias. enter an email address in the <guilabel>Email "
"aliases:</guilabel> field, then click the <guibutton>&plus; Add</guibutton> "
"button"
msgstr ""
"To polje vsebuje psevdonimne naslove, ki prav tako pripadajo tej identiteti "
"(in ne predstavljajo druge identitete). Določite lahko več vzdevkov. Če "
"želite dodati še en vzdevek, v polje <guilabel>Email aliases:</guilabel> "
"vnesite e-poštni naslov, nato pa kliknite gumb <guibutton>&plus; Dodaj</"
"guibutton>"

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Email aliases</title>"
msgstr "<title>Vzdevki pri e-naslovih</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Primary address: first.last@example.org"
msgstr "Primarni naslov: janez.novak@primer.org"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Aliases: first@example.org and last@example.org"
msgstr "Psevdonima: janez@primer.org and novak@primer.org"

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cryptography"
msgstr "Kriptografija"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Identity Cryptography</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kriptografija za identitete</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Identity Cryptography</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kriptografija za identitete</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Identity Cryptography</para>"
msgstr "<para>Kriptografija za identitete</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Cryptography</guilabel> tab allows you to specify the "
"&openpgp; and/or &smime; keys associated with this identity, and to choose "
"the preferred (cryptographic) message format to use."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Kriptografija</guilabel> vam omogoča, da določite ključe "
"&openpgp; in/ali &smime;, povezane s to identiteto, in izberete želeno "
"(kriptografsko) obliko sporočila za uporabo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenPGP signing key:"
msgstr "Ključ za podpisovanje OpenPGP:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you may select an &openpgp; key for signing messages written with this "
"identity in effect. For brevity, only the short key id of selected keys is "
"shown. Hovering over the item will display more information in a tooltip. To "
"select an existing key, use the drop down list. If you wish to create a new "
"public / private key pair, select <guilabel>Generate a new key pair</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko izberete ključ za podpisovanje sporočil, napisanih s to identiteto. "
"Zaradi kratkosti so prikazani le kratki identifikatorji izbranih ključev. Če "
"se z miško pomaknete nad element, se v namigu prikažejo dodatne informacije. "
"Če želite izbrati obstoječi ključ, uporabite spustni seznam. Če želite "
"ustvariti nov par javnih/zasebnih ključev, izberite <guilabel>Generiraj nov "
"par ključev</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenPGP encryption key:"
msgstr "Šifrirni ključ OpenPGP:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you may select an &openpgp; key for encrypting messages when this "
"identity and <xref linkend=\"configure-security-composing-encrypt-to-self\"/"
"> are in effect. This key is also used for the <xref linkend=\"composer-"
"attach-attach-my-public-key\"/> function."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko izberete ključ &openpgp; za šifriranje sporočil, ko sta v veljavi "
"ta identiteta in <xref linkend=\"configure-security-composing-encrypt-to-self"
"\"/>. Ta ključ se uporablja tudi za funkcijo <xref linkend=\"composer-attach-"
"attach-my-public-key\"/>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "&smime; signing certificate:"
msgstr "&smime; potrdilo za podpisovanje:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you may select an x.509 certificate used to sign messages written with "
"this identity in effect. &kmail; cannot generate x.509 certificates. They "
"are issued by certificate authorities. If you have added such a certificate "
"to your key ring, &kmail; can import and use it."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko izberete potrdilo x.509, ki se uporablja za podpisovanje sporočil, "
"napisanih s to veljavno identiteto. &kmail; ne more ustvarjati potrdil "
"x.509. Izdajo jih organi za izdajo potrdil. Če ste takšno potrdilo dodali v "
"obesek za ključe, ga lahko &kmail; uvozi in uporabi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "&smime; encryption certificate:"
msgstr "&smime; potrdilo za enkripcijo:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you may select an x.509 certificate for encrypting messages when this "
"identity and <xref linkend=\"configure-security-composing-encrypt-to-self\"/"
"> are in effect."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko izberete potrdilo x.509 za šifriranje sporočil, ko sta v veljavi ta "
"identiteta in <xref linkend=\"configure-security-composing-encrypt-to-self\"/"
">."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preferred format:"
msgstr "Prednostna oblika:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can choose the default cryptographic message format to use with "
"this identity. You may either select one of the four formats supported by "
"&kmail;, or leave the option at the recommended default setting of "
"<guilabel>Any</guilabel>; this will choose the right format for each "
"recipient you specify, and may create multiple copies of the message, some "
"signed and/or encrypted with an x.509 certificate, and the others signed and/"
"or encrypted with an &openpgp; key."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete privzeto obliko kriptografskega sporočila, ki se bo "
"uporabljala s to identiteto. Izberete lahko eno od štirih oblik, ki jih "
"podpira &kmail;, ali pa pustite priporočeno privzeto nastavitev "
"<guilabel>Katerakoli</guilabel>; to bo izbralo pravo obliko za vsakega "
"prejemnika, ki ga določite, in lahko ustvari več kopij sporočila, nekatere "
"podpisane in/ali šifrirane s potrdilom x.509, druge pa podpisane in/ali "
"šifrirane s ključem &openpgp;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically sign messages:"
msgstr "Samodejno podpisovanje sporočil:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking this box causes &kmail; to affix your digital signature to messages "
"composed by this identity unless this option is manually overridden in the "
"<guilabel>Composer</guilabel> window."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite to polje, bo &kmail; na sporočila, ki jih sestavlja ta "
"identiteta, pritrdil vaš digitalni podpis, razen če je ta možnost ročno "
"prekrita v oknu <guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically encrypt messages:"
msgstr "Samodejno šifriranje sporočil:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking this box causes &kmail; to encrypt messages composed by this "
"identity whenever such encryption is possible (unless overridden in the "
"<guilabel>Composer</guilabel> window)."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite to polje, bo &kmail; šifriral sporočila, ki jih sestavlja ta "
"identiteta, kadarkoli je takšno šifriranje mogoče (razen če je prekrito v "
"oknu <guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Napredno"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Identity Advanced</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Napredno za identiteto</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Identity Advanced</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Napredno za identiteto</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Identity Advanced</para>"
msgstr "<para>napredno za identiteto</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab allows you to specify some "
"infrequently used settings for the identity you're currently editing."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> omogoča določitev nekaterih redko "
"uporabljenih nastavitev za identiteto, ki jo trenutno urejate."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reply-To address:"
msgstr "Naslov za odgovor:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the address to which replies to your messages should be sent. You need "
"this field only if it is different from your normal address (specified using "
"the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> and <guilabel>Email Address</guilabel> fields "
"on the <link linkend=\"configure-identity-general\"><guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> tab</link>), since replies default to the sender's address anyway."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite naslov, na katerega naj se pošiljajo odgovori na vaša sporočila. To "
"polje potrebujete le, če se razlikuje od vašega običajnega naslova "
"(določenega s polji <guilabel>Ime</guilabel> in <guilabel>E-naslov</"
"guilabel> na zavihku <link linkend=\"configure-identity-general"
"\"><guilabel>Splošno</guilabel></link>), saj so odgovori tako ali tako "
"privzeto poslani na naslov pošiljatelja."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This field is useful if you want replies to your mail to go somewhere else "
"than your regular email address, &eg;, if you are using this identity to "
"send messages from an email address that cannot receive replies."
msgstr ""
"To polje je uporabno, če želite, da se odgovori na vašo pošto pošljejo "
"drugam kot na vaš običajni e-poštni naslov, če uporabljate to identiteto za "
"pošiljanje sporočil z e-poštnega naslova, ki ne more prejemati odgovorov."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some mailing lists overwrite this header field with their post address (to "
"ensure that replies go to the list instead of to individuals). So the "
"reliability of this field is limited, and it should be used with caution."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri poštni seznami to polje glave prepišejo s svojim poštnim naslovom "
"(da se zagotovi, da so odgovori poslani seznamu in ne posameznikom). Zato je "
"zanesljivost tega področja omejena in ga je treba uporabljati previdno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "CC addresses:"
msgstr "CC naslovi:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optionally enter one or more addresses, separated by commas, to which carbon "
"copies of your messages should be sent. When you compose a message with this "
"identity, the <guilabel>CC</guilabel> field will be filled with these "
"addresses."
msgstr ""
"Po želji vnesite enega ali več naslovov, ločenih z vejicami, na katere naj "
"se pošiljajo kopije vaših sporočil. Ko sestavite sporočilo s to identiteto, "
"se polje <guilabel>CC</guilabel> napolni s temi naslovi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid "BCC addresses:"
msgstr "BCC naslovi:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optionally enter addresses, separated by commas, to which blind copies of "
"your messages should be sent. When you compose a message with this identity, "
"the <guilabel>BCC</guilabel> field will be filled with these addresses. If "
"you want to send a BCC to the same address for every identity you define, "
"see the <link linkend=\"configure-composer-headers\"><guilabel>Headers</"
"guilabel> tab of the <guilabel>Composer</guilabel> subset</link> (create a "
"custom BCC header)."
msgstr ""
"Po želji vnesite naslove, ločene z vejicami, na katere naj se pošiljajo "
"slepe kopije vaših sporočil. Ko sestavite sporočilo s to identiteto, se "
"polje <guilabel>BCC</guilabel> napolni s temi naslovi. Če želite poslati BCC "
"na isti naslov za vsako opredeljeno identiteto, glejte <link linkend="
"\"configure-composer-headers\"><guilabel>Glave</guilabel> v zavihku "
"<guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel> podsklopa</link> (ustvarite glavo BCC po "
"meri)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dictionary:"
msgstr "Slovar:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the default dictionary for the current identity."
msgstr "Izberite privzeti slovar za trenutno identiteto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sent-mail folder:"
msgstr "Mapa z odposlano pošto:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the folder in which messages should be saved after sending them from "
"this identity. &IMAP; users should consider changing this to an &IMAP; "
"folder, so their sent-mail is stored on a server instead of being stored in "
"a local folder. Then they can access sent messages from a different location."
msgstr ""
"Izberite mapo, v katero naj se shranijo sporočila po pošiljanju iz te "
"identitete. &IMAP; uporabniki bi morali razmisliti o spremembi te mape v "
"mapo &IMAP;, tako da bo njihova poslana pošta shranjena v strežniku in ne v "
"lokalni mapi. Nato lahko do poslanih sporočil dostopajo z druge lokacije."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can exercise more fine-grained control over where to file sent messages "
"by creating a corresponding <link linkend=\"filters\">message filter</link> "
"that is applied to outgoing messages."
msgstr ""
"Natančnejši nadzor nad tem, kam naj se pošljejo sporočila, lahko izvajate "
"tako, da ustvarite ustrezen <link linkend=\"filters\">filter sporočil</"
"link>, ki se uporabi za odhodna sporočila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drafts folder:"
msgstr "Mapa z osnutki:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the folder in which drafts should be saved when using this identity. "
"&IMAP; users should consider changing this to an &IMAP; folder, so their "
"drafts are stored on a server instead of being stored in a local folder. "
"That way they can easily continue to work on their drafts from a different "
"location."
msgstr ""
"Izberite mapo, v katero naj se shranjujejo osnutki pri uporabi te "
"identitete. &IMAP; uporabniki bi morali razmisliti o spremembi te mape v "
"mapo &IMAP;, tako da bodo njihovi osnutki shranjeni na strežniku in ne v "
"lokalni mapi. Tako lahko zlahka nadaljujejo delo s svojimi osnutki na drugem "
"mestu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Templates folder:"
msgstr "Mapa z predlogami:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the folder in which templates should be saved when using this "
"identity. Please see <link linkend=\"new-compose-from-templates\">Compose "
"from templates</link> for more information about templates."
msgstr ""
"Izberite mapo, v katero se shranijo predloge pri uporabi te identitete. Za "
"več informacij o predlogah glejte <link linkend=\"new-compose-from-templates"
"\">Sestavljanje iz predlog</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid "Outgoing Account:"
msgstr "Odhodni račun:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify an alternative &SMTP; / &Sendmail; / &Microsoft; Exchange server to "
"be used when sending messages from this identity."
msgstr ""
"Določite alternativni &SMTP; / &Sendmail; / &Microsoft;strežnik za "
"izmenjavo, ki se bo uporabljal pri pošiljanju sporočil iz te identitete."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need to configure outgoing mail servers first, before you can choose "
"them from the list. You can do this on the <link linkend=\"configure-"
"accounts-sending\"><guilabel>Sending</guilabel> tab</link> of the <link "
"linkend=\"configure-accounts\"> <guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> page</link>."
msgstr ""
"Najprej morate konfigurirati strežnike odhodne pošte, preden jih lahko "
"izberete s seznama. To lahko storite na zavihku <link linkend=\"configure-"
"accounts-sending\"><guilabel>Pošiljanje</guilabel></link> <link linkend="
"\"configure-accounts\"> stran <guilabel>Uporabniški računi</guilabel ></"
"link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attach my vCard to message"
msgstr "Sporočilu priložite moj vCard"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose this option if you want to attach a vCard file to each message sent "
"from this identity. A short dialog will ensue."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite datoteko vCard priložiti vsakemu sporočilu, "
"poslanemu iz te identitete. Sledil bo kratek dialog."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option opens a dialog just like the <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook/"
"editing-contact-data.html\">&kaddressbook; Adding Contact Data</ulink> "
"dialog. Enter your name, email address, &etc;, then click <guilabel>OK</"
"guilabel> to create a new vCard."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost odpre pogovorno okno, podobno kot pogovorno okno <ulink url="
"\"help:/kaddressbook/editing-contact-data.html\">&kaddressbook; Dodajanje "
"kontaktnih podatkov</ulink>. Vnesite svoje ime, e-poštni naslov in podobno, "
"nato pa kliknite <guilabel>OK</guilabel>, da ustvarite novo kartico vCard."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "From existing vCard"
msgstr "Iz že obstoječe vCard"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option opens a browse directories dialog which allows you to to select "
"a .vcf file. (Hint: Use &kaddressbook; to export a vCard file that can be "
"used here.)"
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost odpre pogovorno okno za pregledovanje imenikov, v katerem lahko "
"izberete datoteko .vcf. (Namig: Za izvoz datoteke vCard, ki jo lahko "
"uporabite v tem primeru, uporabite &kaddressbook;.)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duplicate existing vCard"
msgstr "Podvajanje obstoječe kartice vCard"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option opens a drop down list of all the other identities already "
"defined, so you may select the vCard associated with one of them."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost odpre spustni seznam vseh drugih že opredeljenih identitet, tako "
"da lahko izberete kartico vCard, povezano z eno od njih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autocorrection language:"
msgstr "Jezik samodejnega popravljanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the drop down list to select the language associated with the optional "
"autocorrection tool when using this identity."
msgstr ""
"S spustnim seznamom izberite jezik, povezan z izbirnim orodjem za samodejno "
"popravljanje, ko uporabljate to identiteto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default domain:"
msgstr "Privzeta domena:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This field is filled with the value from the <filename>hostnames</filename> "
"file (in /etc) by default. The <guilabel>Composer</guilabel> will append "
"this domain name to any purely local email address you specify. This feature "
"is primarily useful in a &Sendmail; environment."
msgstr ""
"To polje je privzeto izpolnjeno z vrednostjo iz datoteke <filename>naslova "
"gostiteljev</filename> (v /etc). <guilabel>Composer</guilabel> bo to ime "
"domene dodal kateremu koli izključno lokalnemu e-poštnemu naslovu, ki ga "
"določite. Ta funkcija je uporabna predvsem v okolju &Sendmail;."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default domain"
msgstr "Privzeta domena"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Default domain set to <userinput>kde.org</userinput>; \"To:\" address set to "
"<userinput>foo</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta domena je nastavljena na <userinput>kde.org</userinput>; naslov "
"\"Za:\" je nastavljen na <userinput>foo</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Composer</guilabel> sends the message to foo@kde.org."
msgstr "<guilabel>Composer</guilabel> pošlje sporočilo na naslov foo@kde.org."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "Templates"
msgstr "Predloge"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Identity Templates</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Predloge identitet</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Identity Templates</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Predloge identitet</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Identity Templates</para>"
msgstr "<para>Predloge identitet</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you may create and manage custom templates for this identity to use "
"when composing new messages, replying to someone, or forwarding messages "
"inline. The message templates support substitution commands. You may simply "
"type them in, or select them from the <guimenu>Insert Command "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guimenu> menu. Three kinds of "
"commands are provided."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko ustvarite in upravljate predloge po meri za to identiteto, ki se "
"uporabljajo pri sestavljanju novih sporočil, odgovarjanju nekomu ali "
"posredovanju sporočil v vrstici. Predloge sporočil podpirajo ukaze za "
"zamenjavo. Lahko jih preprosto vnesete ali izberete iz menija "
"<guimenu>Vstavi ukaz <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guimenu>. Na voljo so tri vrste ukazov."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Original Message &gt;</guilabel> / <guilabel>Current Message &gt;</"
"guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prvotno sporočilo &gt;</guilabel> / <guilabel>Trenutno sporočilo "
"&gt;</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These commands extract information from the message you're replying to, or "
"forwarding, and insert that information into the composition window."
msgstr ""
"Ti ukazi iz sporočila, na katerega odgovarjate ali ga posredujete, izvlečejo "
"informacije in jih vstavijo v okno za sestavljanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid "Process with External Programs &gt;"
msgstr "Proces z zunanjimi programi &gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These commands will pipe the message to which you are responding through an "
"external program, then insert the output into &kmail;'s composition window."
msgstr ""
"Ti ukazi bodo sporočilo, na katerega odgovarjate, posredovali prek zunanjega "
"programa, nato pa bodo izhod vstavili v okno za sestavljanje sporočila "
"&kmail;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous &gt;"
msgstr "Razno &gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These commands perform functions like choosing the dictionary the spell "
"checker should use, or inserting the contents of a text file into the "
"composition window."
msgstr ""
"Ti ukazi opravljajo funkcije, kot je izbira slovarja, ki naj ga uporablja "
"program za preverjanje črkovanja, ali vstavljanje vsebine besedilne datoteke "
"v okno za sestavljanje."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Quote indicator:</guilabel> field allows you to override the "
"default quotation indicator character \"&gt;\". The <guibutton>Copy Global "
"Templates</guibutton> button will reset all the custom templates defined "
"here to &kmail;'s defaults. (You can achieve the same end result by "
"unselecting the <guilabel>Use custom message templates for this identity</"
"guilabel> check box at the top left of this dialog box.)"
msgstr ""
"Polje <guilabel>Kazalec citata:</guilabel> vam omogoča, da razveljavite "
"privzeti znak kazalca citata \"&gt;\". Gumb <guibutton>Kopiraj splošne "
"predloge</guibutton> ponastavi vse tukaj opredeljene predloge po meri na "
"privzete nastavitve &kmail;. (Enak končni rezultat lahko dosežete tako, da "
"ne izberete potrditvenega polja <guilabel>a to identiteto uporabi predloge "
"sporočil po meri</guilabel> v zgornjem levem kotu tega pogovornega okna.)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Templates specified here are identity-specific. They override global "
"templates, but can be overridden by folder-specific templates if those are "
"specified."
msgstr ""
"Tu navedene predloge so specifične za posamezno identiteto. Prevladajo nad "
"splošnimi predlogami, vendar jih lahko prevladajo predloge za posamezne "
"mape, če so te določene."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid "Signature"
msgstr "Podpis"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Identity Signature</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Identitetni podpis</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Identity Signature</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Identitetni podpis</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Identity Signature</para>"
msgstr "<para>Identitetni podpis</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to specify a signature (sometimes called <quote>footer</"
"quote> or <quote>disclaimer</quote>) to be appended to each message sent "
"from this identity."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku lahko določite podpis (včasih imenovan <quote>noga</quote> ali "
"<quote>opozorilo</quote>), ki se doda vsakemu sporočilu, poslanemu s te "
"identitete."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This type of signature has nothing to do with the (digital) signatures "
"discussed in the <link linkend=\"configure-identity-cryptography"
"\">Cryptography</link> section. It is a bit confusing to call this a "
"signature, but since the term is already used everywhere else, we keep this "
"nomenclature. Just remember that these \"signatures\" and digital signatures "
"are two completely different things."
msgstr ""
"Ta vrsta podpisa nima nič skupnega z (digitalnimi) podpisi, obravnavanimi v "
"razdelku <link linkend=\"configure-identity-cryptography\">Kriptografija</"
"link>. Nekoliko zmedeno je to imenovati podpis, vendar ker se ta izraz že "
"uporablja povsod drugje, ohranjamo to poimenovanje. Ne pozabite, da so ti "
"\"podpisi\" in digitalni podpisi dve popolnoma različni stvari."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the <guilabel>Enable signature</guilabel> option if you want &kmail; "
"to append a signature when using this identity. To <emphasis>automatically</"
"emphasis> append it to every new message you must also select "
"<guilabel>Automatically insert signature</guilabel> option on the "
"<guilabel>Composer</guilabel> configuration page."
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Vključi podpis</guilabel>, če želite, da &kmail; "
"pri uporabi te identitete doda podpis. Če ga želite <emphasis>avtomatsko</"
"emphasis> dodati vsakemu novemu sporočilu, morate izbrati tudi možnost "
"<guilabel>Automatsko vstavi podpis</guilabel> na konfiguracijski strani "
"<guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel>-ja."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; can obtain the signature text from various sources. The default is "
"<guilabel>Input Field Below</guilabel>. Just enter your signature in the "
"textbox. If you want to use rich text, select the <guilabel>Use &HTML;</"
"guilabel> checkbox at the lower left. A formatting toolbar will then appear."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; lahko besedilo podpisa pridobite iz različnih virov. Privzeto je "
"<guilabel>Vhodno polje spodaj</guilabel>. V besedilno polje vpišite svoj "
"podpis. Če želite uporabiti bogato besedilo, izberite potrditveno polje "
"<guilabel>Uporabi &HTML;</guilabel> spodaj levo. Nato se prikaže orodna "
"vrstica za oblikovanje."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The traditional procedure in Unix is to read the text from a file called "
"<filename>.signature</filename> in your home folder. This file may be shared "
"among several programs, so the same signature appears in every email program "
"you use. To do this, select <guilabel>File</guilabel> from the "
"<guilabel>Obtain Signature text from:</guilabel> drop down menu. If you want "
"to edit the file, click the <guilabel>Edit File</guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Tradicionalni postopek v Unixu je branje besedila iz datoteke z imenom "
"<filename>.signature</filename> v domači mapi. Ta datoteka je lahko deljena "
"med več programi, tako da je enak podpis prikazan v vseh e-poštnih "
"programih, ki jih uporabljate. To storite tako, da v spustnem meniju "
"<guilabel>Pridobi besedilo podpisa iz:</guilabel> izberete "
"<guilabel>Datoteka</guilabel>. Če želite urediti datoteko, kliknite gumb "
"<guilabel>Urejanje datoteke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; can also read the signature text from the output of a command. You "
"can use programs such as <command>fortune</command> to create a randomly "
"selected signature for each new message. Everything the program prints onto "
"<acronym>stdout</acronym> is caught and used as the signature text. To read "
"the text from the output of a command, select the <guilabel>Output of "
"Command</guilabel> option. Enter the command (with full path) in the "
"<guilabel>Specify command:</guilabel> edit field."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; lahko besedilo podpisa prebere tudi iz izpisa ukaza. S programi, kot "
"je <command>usoda (fortune)</command>, lahko za vsako novo sporočilo "
"ustvarite naključno izbran podpis. Vse, kar program izpiše v "
"<acronym>stdout</acronym>, se ujame in uporabi kot besedilo podpisa. Če "
"želite prebrati besedilo iz izpisa ukaza, izberite možnost <guilabel>Izpis "
"ukaza</guilabel>. Ukaz (s celotno potjo) vnesite v urejevalno polje "
"<guilabel>Opredelite ukaz:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the Internet, signatures are by convention separated from the body of the "
"message by a line containing only the three characters <quote>-- </quote> "
"(dash, dash, space). If the <guilabel>Prepend separator to signature</"
"guilabel> option has been set in the <guilabel>Composer</guilabel> "
"configuration, &kmail; will automatically prepend this line to the signature "
"text (unless it is already present)."
msgstr ""
"Na internetu so podpisi po dogovoru ločeni od besedila sporočila z vrstico, "
"ki vsebuje le tri znake <quote>-- </quote> (pomišljaj, pomišljaj, "
"presledek). Če je v konfiguraciji <guilabel>Sestavljalnik</guilabel> "
"nastavljena možnost <guilabel>Predpisovanje ločilnika v podpis</guilabel>, "
"bo &kmail; to vrstico samodejno dodal besedilu podpisa (razen če je že "
"prisotna)."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid "Picture"
msgstr "Slika"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Identity Picture</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Slika identitete</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Identity Picture</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Slika identitete</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Identity Picture</para>"
msgstr "<para>Slika identitete</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; can send a small (48x48 pixels), low-quality, monochrome picture "
"with every message. For example, this could be a picture of you, or a glyph. "
"It is shown in the recipient's mail client (if supported)."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; z vsakim sporočilom lahko pošljete majhno enobarvno sliko (48x48 "
"slikovnih pik) nizke kakovosti. To je lahko na primer vaša slika ali glif. "
"Prikaže se v prejemnikovem poštnem odjemalcu (če jo podpira)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send picture with every message"
msgstr "Pošlji sliko z vsakim sporočilom"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box if you want &kmail; to add a so-called X-Face header to "
"messages written with this identity. An X-Face is a small (48x48 pixels) "
"black and white image that some mail clients are able to display."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite, da &kmail; doda tako imenovano glavo X-Face "
"sporočilom, napisanim s to identiteto. Obraz X je majhna (48x48 slikovnih "
"pik) črno-bela slika, ki jo lahko prikažejo nekateri poštni odjemalci."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid "Obtain picture from:"
msgstr "Pridobi sliko iz:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "This drop down list gives you two ways to select an image."
msgstr "Ta spustni seznam omogoča dva načina izbire slike."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>External Source <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guilabel> (the default)"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zunanji vir <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guilabel> (privzeto)"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: configure.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select File..."
msgstr "Izberite datoteko..."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this button to select an image file from which to create the picture. "
"Use a high-contrast image that is square, or nearly square. A light "
"background helps improve the result."
msgstr ""
"S tem gumbom izberete slikovno datoteko, iz katere želite ustvariti sliko. "
"Uporabite sliko z visokim kontrastom, ki je kvadratna ali skoraj kvadratna. "
"Svetlo ozadje pripomore k boljšemu rezultatu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: configure.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set From Address Book"
msgstr "Nastavitev iz imenika"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may use this button to create a scaled-down version of the picture you "
"have set in your own address book entry."
msgstr ""
"S tem gumbom lahko ustvarite pomanjšano različico slike, ki ste jo nastavili "
"v svojem vnosu v imeniku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "Input Field Below"
msgstr "Vnosno polje spodaj"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this option to enter an arbitrary X-Face string. Examples are available "
"at <ulink url=\"https://ace.home.xs4all.nl/X-Faces/\">https://ace.home."
"xs4all.nl/X-Faces/</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"To možnost uporabite za vnos poljubnega niza X-Face. Primeri so na voljo na "
"<ulink url=\"https://ace.home.xs4all.nl/X-Faces/\">https://ace.home.xs4all."
"nl/X-Faces/</ulink>"

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email Accounts"
msgstr "E-poštni računi"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find a quick introduction to both sending and receiving accounts in "
"the <link linkend=\"setting-up-your-account\">Setting up your Account</link> "
"section."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <link linkend=\"setting-up-your-account\">Nastavitev računa</"
"link> najdete kratko predstavitev računov za pošiljanje in prejemanje."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page allows you to create one or more (incoming and outgoing) "
"<emphasis>accounts</emphasis>, &ie;, combinations of mail servers, login "
"information, and other settings. Typically, you will create one outgoing "
"(used for sending messages) and one incoming (used to retrieve messages) "
"account. You may create as many accounts as you want, though, and assign "
"each one to a different <link linkend=\"configure-identity\">identity</"
"link>. Or you may set up just one identity, and decide which account to use "
"each time you compose a message. This page also lets you set up one or more "
"<acronym>LDAP</acronym> (Lightweight Directory Access Protocol) servers."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani lahko ustvarite enega ali več (dohodnih in odhodnih) "
"<emphasis>računov</emphasis>, &ie;, kombinacij poštnih strežnikov, prijavnih "
"podatkov in drugih nastavitev. Običajno ustvarite en odhodni (ki se "
"uporablja za pošiljanje sporočil) in en dohodni račun (ki se uporablja za "
"prejemanje sporočil). Ustvarite lahko poljubno število računov in vsakega "
"dodelite drugi <link linkend=\"configure-identity\">identiteti</link>. Lahko "
"pa nastavite samo eno identiteto in se odločite, kateri račun boste "
"uporabili vsakič, ko boste ustvarili sporočilo. Na tej strani lahko "
"nastavite tudi enega ali več strežnikov <acronym>LDAP</acronym> (Lightweight "
"Directory Access Protocol)."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid "Receiving"
msgstr "Prejemanje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Receiving Account</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Račun za prejemanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Receiving Account</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Račun za prejemanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Receiving Account Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek računa za prejemanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For basic information, see <link linkend=\"receiving-mail\">Setting up your "
"Account: Receiving</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za osnovne informacije glejte <link linkend=\"receiving-mail\">Nastavitev "
"računa: prejemanje</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The column of buttons on the right let you <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> a "
"new account, and <guibutton>Modify</guibutton> or <guilabel>Remove</"
"guilabel> an existing account. You ought not modify or remove the "
"<guilabel>Local Folders</guilabel> entry, which is present by default. The "
"<guilabel>Restart</guilabel> button will simulate a program restart."
msgstr ""
"Stolpec gumbov na desni strani omogoča <guibutton>Dodaj...</guibutton> nov "
"račun in <guibutton>spremeni</guibutton> ali <guilabel>odstrani</guilabel> "
"obstoječi račun. Vnosa <guilabel>krajevne mape</guilabel>, ki je privzeto "
"prisoten, ne smete spreminjati ali odstraniti. Gumb <guilabel>Ponovni zagon</"
"guilabel> simulira ponovni zagon programa."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Customize Accounts Order...</guibutton> button opens a dialog "
"that lets you move any IMAP accounts you have created, and the group of "
"accounts associated with <guilabel>Local Folders</guilabel>, higher or lower "
"in the list."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Prilagajanje vrstnega reda računov...</guibutton> odpre "
"pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko vse ustvarjene račune IMAP in skupino "
"računov, povezanih s <guilabel>Krajevnimi mapami</guilabel>, premaknete "
"višje ali nižje na seznamu."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Retrieval Options</guilabel> popup menu for each account lets "
"you specify whether &kmail; should check for new mail immediately after it "
"has been started. You may also select <guilabel>Include in Manual Mail "
"Check</guilabel> and <guilabel>Switch offline on &kmail; Shutdown</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"V priročnem meniju <guilabel>Možnosti pridobivanja</guilabel> za vsak račun "
"lahko določite, ali naj &kmail; preveri novo pošto takoj po zagonu. Izberete "
"lahko tudi <guilabel>Vključi v ročno preverjanje pošte</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Preklopi v stanje brez povezave ob izklopu &kmail; </guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Detailed new mail notification</guilabel> is enabled then "
"&kmail; will show the number of new messages for each folder provided you "
"have chosen to be notified with a dialog. More advanced notification "
"options, like playing a sound or synthesizing speech, are available via the "
"<guibutton>Other Actions</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno <guilabel>Podrobno obveščanje o novi pošti</guilabel>, bo "
"&kmail; prikazal število novih sporočil za vsako mapo, če ste izbrali "
"možnost obveščanja s pogovornim oknom. Naprednejše možnosti obveščanja, kot "
"je predvajanje zvoka ali sintetiziranje govora, so na voljo prek gumba "
"<guibutton>Druga dejanja</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sending"
msgstr "Pošiljanje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Sending Account</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Račun za pošiljanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Sending Account</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Račun za pošiljanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Sending Account Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek računa za pošiljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Sending</guilabel> tab lets you define new outgoing mail "
"servers, and also set some options that affect all the messages you send."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Pošiljanje</guilabel> lahko določite nove strežnike za "
"odhodno pošto in nastavite nekatere možnosti, ki vplivajo na vsa poslana "
"sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For basic information, see <link linkend=\"sending-mail\">Setting up your "
"Account: Sending</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za osnovne informacije glejte <link linkend=\"sending-mail\">Nastavitev "
"računa: pošiljanje</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> or <guibutton>Modify...</"
"guibutton> the <guilabel>Create Outgoing Account</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Configure account</guilabel> dialogs will open respectively. For "
"sending via &Sendmail; or similar programs you may specify a name and the "
"location of the &Sendmail; program. For &SMTP; you must specify the "
"<guilabel>Name</guilabel>, <guilabel>Outgoing mail server</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>Port</guilabel> of the server. <guilabel>Server requires "
"authentication</guilabel> will enable the <guilabel>Login</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Password</guilabel> fields. If you are not sure about the security "
"settings, you should make &kmail; test for the best settings by using "
"<guibutton>Auto Detect</guibutton> on the <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete <guibutton>Dodaj...</guibutton> ali <guibutton>spremeni...</"
"guibutton>, se odpreta pogovorni okni <guilabel>Ustvari odhodni račun</"
"guilabel> oziroma <guilabel>Konfiguriraj račun</guilabel>. Za pošiljanje "
"prek programa &Sendmail; ali podobnih programov lahko določite ime in "
"lokacijo programa &Sendmail;. Za &SMTP; morate določiti <guilabel>Ime</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Server izhodne pošte</guilabel> in <guilabel>Vhod</"
"guilabel> strežnika. <guilabel>Strežnik zahteva preverjanje pristnosti</"
"guilabel> in bo omogočil polji <guilabel>Prijava</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Geslo</guilabel>. Če niste prepričani o varnostnih nastavitvah, "
"morate z uporabo gumba <guibutton>Automatsko zaznaj</guibutton> na zavihku "
"<guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> preveriti najboljše nastavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Before sending</guilabel> section, <guilabel>Confirm "
"action</guilabel> will pop up a confirmation box every time you send a "
"message, while <guilabel>Check spelling</guilabel> will invoke the spell "
"checker before a message is sent."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Pred pošiljanjem</guilabel> bo <guilabel>Potrdi "
"dejanje</guilabel> ob vsakem pošiljanju sporočila prikazal potrditveno okno, "
"<guilabel>Preveri črkovanje</guilabel> pa bo pred pošiljanjem sporočila "
"sprožil preverjanje črkovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Send messages in outbox folder</guilabel> lets you specify when "
"queued messages, &ie;, messages in the outbox folder waiting to be sent, "
"should be dispatched. You may choose among three options."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Poslati sporočila v mapo Prejeto</guilabel> vam omogoča, da "
"določite, kdaj naj se pošljejo sporočila v čakalni vrsti, &ie;, sporočila v "
"mapi Prejeto, ki čakajo na pošiljanje. Izbirate lahko med tremi možnostmi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid "Never Automatically"
msgstr "Nikoli samodejno"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Queued messages will only be sent if you select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Send queued messages</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Sporočila v čakalni vrsti bodo poslana le, če izberete možnost "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka </guimenu><guimenuitem>Poslati sporočila v "
"čakalni vrsti</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:831
#, no-c-format
msgid "On Manual Mail Checks"
msgstr "Ob ročnem preglejevanju pošte"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Queued messages will be sent after you have manually checked for new mail, "
"&eg; with <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Check Mail</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Of course, you may also send the queued messages "
"manually via <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send queued "
"messages</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Sporočila v čakalni vrsti bodo poslana, ko boste ročno preverili novo pošto, "
"&eg; z <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preveri pošto</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Seveda lahko sporočila v čakalni vrsti pošljete "
"tudi ročno prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji "
"sporočila v čakalni vrsti</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid "On All Mail Checks"
msgstr "Vsakič ob preverjanju pošte"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Queued messages will be sent after every check for new mail, &ie;, after "
"automatic mail checks, and also after manual mail checks. Of course, you may "
"also send the queued messages manually via <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Send queued messages</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Sporočila v čakalni vrsti bodo poslana po vsakem preverjanju nove pošte, "
"&ie;, po samodejnem preverjanju pošte in tudi po ročnem preverjanju pošte. "
"Seveda lahko sporočila v čakalni vrsti pošljete tudi ročno prek "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji sporočila v "
"čakalni vrsti</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default send method:</guilabel> lets you define what happens when "
"a message is sent. If <guilabel>Send now</guilabel> is selected, the message "
"is sent to the mail server immediately. If <guilabel>Send later</guilabel> "
"is selected, the message is queued in the outbox to be sent later with the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Queued Messages</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> command, or automatically when you check your "
"mail, depending on the setting chosen for <guilabel>Send messages in outbox "
"folder</guilabel>, above."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeti način pošiljanja</guilabel> vam omogoča nastavljanja "
"dogodkov, ki se zgodijo pri pošiljanju sporočila. Če označite "
"<guilabel>Pošlji zdaj</guilabel>, bo sporočilo poslano strežniku takoj, "
"metoda <guilabel>Pošlji kasneje</guilabel> pa sporočilo uvrsti v čakalno "
"vrsto. Za procesiranje čakalne vrste izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpošlji čakajoča sporočila</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"Odpošiljanje čakajoče pošte sproži tudi ukaz za preverjanje pošte, če je le "
"tako nastavljeno v nastavitvenem razdelku <guilabel>Razno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Enable Undo Send:</guilabel> checkbox lets you specify an "
"interval of time (from 10 to 50 seconds) during which you may abort mail "
"transport. Your message will be queued, and a small <guibutton>Undo Send</"
"guibutton> button will appear in the notification area. Click the button (in "
"time) to stop the message from being sent."
msgstr ""
"S potrditvenim poljem <guilabel>Omogoči razveljavljanje pošiljanja:</"
"guilabel> lahko določite časovni interval (od 10 do 50 sekund), v katerem "
"lahko prekinete prenos pošte. Vaše sporočilo bo uvrščeno v čakalno vrsto, v "
"območju za obvestila pa se bo pojavil majhen <guibutton>Prekliči pošiljanje</"
"guibutton>. Kliknite gumb (pravočasno), da ustavite pošiljanje sporočila."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:867
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>LDAP Servers</title>"
msgstr "<title>LDAP Strežniki</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>LDAP Servers</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>LDAP Strežniki</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>LDAP Servers</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>LDAP Strežniki</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid "The LDAP Servers Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek LDAP Strežniki"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this dialog to configure any LDAP servers you wish to access. Please "
"consult the <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook/configure-ldap-server.html"
"\">&kaddressbook; Appendix</ulink> for more details."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko konfigurirate vse strežnike LDAP, do katerih "
"želite dostopati. Za več podrobnosti si oglejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kaddressbook/configure-ldap-server.html\">&kaddressbook; Dodatek</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid "Appearance Page"
msgstr "Stran z videzom"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Appearance page lets you adjust many aspects of &kmail;'s graphical user "
"interface, including color schemes, font selection, and even the physical "
"arrangement of the message list in the main window."
msgstr ""
"Na strani Videz lahko prilagodite številne vidike grafičnega uporabniškega "
"vmesnika programa &kmail;, vključno z barvnimi shemami, izbiro pisave in "
"celo fizično postavitvijo seznama sporočil v glavnem oknu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Appearance General</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Splošno za videz</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:908 configure.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Appearance General</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Splošno za videz</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:911
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Appearance (General) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek videz (splošno)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Close message window after replying or forwarding</"
"guilabel> option is activated, &kmail; will close the separate message "
"window when a composer window (for a reply, or to forward the message) is "
"opened. <guilabel>Enable access key</guilabel> is selected by default. "
"Access keys allow you to use the keyboard for functions normally done with "
"the mouse, such as following links. For more information see <ulink url="
"\"help:/konqueror/accesskeys.html\">Access keys</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če je aktivirana možnost <guilabel>Zapri okno sporočila po odgovoru ali "
"posredovanju</guilabel>, bo &kmail; zaprl ločeno okno sporočila, ko se odpre "
"okno sestavljalca (za odgovor ali posredovanje sporočila). <guilabel>Vključi "
"ključ za dostop</guilabel> je privzeto izbran. Tipke za dostop omogočajo "
"uporabo tipkovnice za funkcije, ki se običajno izvajajo z miško, na primer "
"sledenje povezavam. Za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"help:/konqueror/"
"accesskeys.html\">Dostopne tipke</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable <guilabel>Reduce font size for quoted text</guilabel> to show quoted "
"text (in a reply) with a smaller type face. <guilabel>Show expand/collapse "
"quote marks</guilabel> displays little widgets along with each bit of quoted "
"text. These allow you to show (+) or hide (-) nested quotes beyond a certain "
"level. This is useful in protracted email conversations where nobody deletes "
"what has gone before."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite možnost <guilabel>Zmanjšanje velikosti pisave za citirano "
"besedilo</guilabel> za prikaz citiranega besedila (v odgovoru) z manjšo "
"velikostjo pisave. <guilabel>Prikaži razširitev/z narekovajev</guilabel> "
"prikaže majhne gradnike ob vsakem delu citiranega besedila. Z njimi lahko "
"prikažete (+) ali skrijete (-) ugnezdene narekovaje nad določeno ravnjo. To "
"je uporabno pri dolgotrajnih e-poštnih pogovorih, ko nihče ne izbriše "
"prejšnjih pogovorov."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing <guilabel>Override character encoding:</guilabel> from its default "
"value <guilabel>Auto</guilabel> will force the use of the specified encoding "
"for all messages, no matter what the &MIME; headers say. <guilabel>Minimum "
"font size:</guilabel> lets you control the smallest font &kmail; will use. "
"Set this higher if you have trouble reading really small fonts."
msgstr ""
"Če spremenite <guilabel>Povozi kodiranje znakov:</guilabel> s privzete "
"vrednosti <guilabel>Auto</guilabel>, se bo za vsa sporočila uporabilo "
"določeno kodiranje, ne glede na to, kaj piše v glavi &MIME;. "
"<guilabel>Najmanjša velikost pisave:</guilabel> omogoča nadzor najmanjše "
"pisave, ki jo bo &kmail; uporabil. Če imate težave z branjem zelo majhnih "
"pisav, nastavite višjo vrednost."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>System Tray</guilabel> provides three ways to control &kmail;'s "
"interaction with the &kde; task bar / panel. If <guilabel>Enable system tray "
"icon</guilabel> is selected, a small icon "
"(<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-mark-unread.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>) will be displayed in the "
"system tray area. If <guilabel>Start minimized to tray</guilabel> is "
"activated, only this icon will appear when &kmail; is launched. Selecting "
"<guilabel>Show unread email in taskbar</guilabel> causes the number of "
"currently unread messages to appear on &kmail;'s taskbar button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sistemska vrstica</guilabel> omogoča tri načine za nadzor "
"interakcije &kmail; s &kde; opravilno vrstico / ploščo. Če je izbrana "
"možnost <guilabel>Omogoči ikono v sistemski vrstici</guilabel>, se v območju "
"sistemske vrstice prikaže majhna ikona "
"(<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-mark-unread.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>). Če je aktivirana "
"možnost <guilabel>Začni minimizirano na pladnju</guilabel>, se bo ob zagonu "
"programa &kmail; prikazala samo ta ikona. Če izberete možnost "
"<guilabel>Pokaži neprebrano e-pošto v opravilni vrstici</guilabel>, se "
"število trenutno neprebranih sporočil prikaže na gumbu &kmail; v opravilni "
"vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the icon is visible, you may hide &kmail;'s main window either by "
"clicking on the icon or by clicking on the window's close button. Clicking "
"on the icon will make &kmail;'s main window visible again. If you click on "
"the icon with the &RMB;, a context menu will appear. You can check for new "
"mail, create a new message, or quit &kmail;. If there are any unread "
"messages, the entry <guilabel>New Messages In &gt;</guilabel> will appear, "
"along with a list of the folders containing unread messages. Select one of "
"these folders, and it will be opened in &kmail;'s main window."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ikona vidna, lahko skrijete glavno okno &kmail; s klikom na ikono ali "
"s klikom na gumb za zapiranje okna. S klikom na ikono bo glavno okno "
"storitve &kmail; spet vidno. Če kliknete na ikono z znakom &RMB;, se prikaže "
"kontekstni meni. Preverite lahko novo pošto, ustvarite novo sporočilo ali "
"zaključite program &kmail;. Če so na voljo neprebrana sporočila, se prikaže "
"vnos <guilabel>Nova sporočila v &gt;</guilabel> skupaj s seznamom map, ki "
"vsebujejo neprebrana sporočila. Izberite eno od teh map in odprla se bo v "
"glavnem oknu storitve &kmail;."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:975
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts"
msgstr "Pisave"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid "Appearance Fonts"
msgstr "Videz pisav"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Appearance (Fonts) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek za videz pisav"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section lets you tailor the fonts &kmail; uses. Select <guilabel>Use "
"custom fonts</guilabel> to activate the dialog. Apply to: <guilabel>Message "
"Body</guilabel> sets the font for the reader pane. The <guilabel>Composer</"
"guilabel> option sets the font in which new plain text messages are shown "
"while they are being written. <guilabel>Message List</guilabel> changes the "
"font used to display the message list. You can also choose special fonts for "
"Unread, Important, and Action Item message list entries. <guilabel>Printing "
"Output</guilabel> alters the font used when printing. <guilabel>Fixed Width "
"Font</guilabel> affects the display of some &HTML; messages."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku lahko prilagodite pisave, ki jih &kmail; uporablja. Izberite "
"<guilabel>Uporabi pisave po meni</guilabel>, da aktivirate pogovorno okno. "
"Uporabi za: <guilabel>Telo sporočila</guilabel> nastavi pisavo za podokno "
"bralnika. Možnost <guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel> določa pisavo, v kateri se "
"med pisanjem prikazujejo nova sporočila v navadnem besedilu. "
"<guilabel>Seznam sporočil</guilabel> spremeni pisavo, ki se uporablja za "
"prikaz seznama sporočil. Izberete lahko tudi posebne pisave za vnose na "
"seznamu neprebranih, pomembnih in akcijskih sporočil. <guilabel>Izhod "
"tiskanja</guilabel> spreminja pisavo, ki se uporablja pri tiskanju. "
"<guilabel>Pisava stalne širine</guilabel> vpliva na prikaz nekaterih "
"sporočil &HTML;."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show only monospaced fonts</guilabel> restricts the number of "
"fonts available. Only the names of fixed-width fonts will be displayed when "
"this option is in effect."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži samo enoštevilčne pisave</guilabel> omeji število pisav, ki "
"so na voljo. Ko je ta možnost v veljavi, so prikazana samo imena pisav s "
"fiksno širino."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Barve"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1014
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Appearance Colors</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Videz barv</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Appearance Colors</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Videz barv</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Appearance (Colors) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek videz (za barve)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1028
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section allows you to change the color of a few things by double "
"clicking on an entry in the list box. Select <guilabel>Use custom colors</"
"guilabel> to activate this feature. Select <guilabel>Do not change color "
"from original HTML mail</guilabel> to preserve the color scheme selected by "
"the sender of any &HTML; message."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku lahko spremenite barvo nekaterih stvari tako, da dvakrat "
"kliknete na vnos v polju seznama. Če želite aktivirati to funkcijo, izberite "
"<guilabel>Uporabi barve po meri</guilabel>. Izberite <guilabel>Ne spreminjaj "
"barve iz prvotne pošte HTML</guilabel>, če želite ohraniti barvno shemo, ki "
"jo je izbral pošiljatelj sporočila &HTML;."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Recycle colors on deep quoting</guilabel> will restart the quote "
"coloring at the first level after the third level of quoting has been "
"reached. Note that the <guilabel>Quoted text</guilabel> colors only work in "
"the message reader, not in the composer. If you want folders which are "
"getting close to their quota (space allotment, used on &IMAP; servers) to be "
"displayed in a different color, you may specify a percentage value as a "
"threshold."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Recikliranje barv pri globokem citiranju</guilabel> bo po doseženi "
"tretji stopnji citiranja ponovno začel barvati citiranje kot na prvi stopnji "
"(in nato drugi, tretji in spet prvi ...). Upoštevajte, da barve "
"<guilabel>Citiranega besedila</guilabel> delujejo samo v bralniku sporočil "
"in ne v sestavljalniku. Če želite, da se mape, ki se približujejo svoji "
"kvoti (dodeljeni prostor, ki se uporablja v strežnikih &IMAP;), prikažejo v "
"drugačni barvi, lahko kot prag določite odstotno vrednost."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid "Layout"
msgstr "Razpored"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1045
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Default Layout</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Privzeti razpored</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Default Layout</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Privzeti razpored</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1054
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Appearance (Layout) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek videz (za razpored)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1059
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab lets you configure the layout of &kmail;'s main window."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku lahko nastavite postavitev glavnega okna storitve &kmail;."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Folder List</guilabel> section you may choose between the "
"<guilabel>Long folder list</guilabel> (default option), which uses the full "
"height of the window, and the <guilabel>Short folder list</guilabel>. With "
"the <guilabel>Short</guilabel> option, if you have selected <guilabel>Show "
"the message preview pane below the message list</guilabel>, the message list "
"and the folder list will occupy a horizontal strip, with the message preview "
"pane using the entire bottom portion of the window. If you have selected "
"<guilabel>Show the message preview pane next to the message list</guilabel>, "
"the folder list and the message list will occupy a vertical strip, with the "
"message preview pane on the right."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Splet map</guilabel> lahko izbirate med "
"<guilabel>Dolgim seznamom map</guilabel> (privzeta možnost), ki uporablja "
"celotno višino okna, in <guilabel>Kratkim seznamom map</guilabel>. Če ste z "
"možnostjo <guilabel>Kratek</guilabel> izbrali možnost <guilabel>Pokaži "
"podokno za predogled sporočil pod seznamom sporočil</guilabel>, bosta seznam "
"sporočil in seznam map zavzemala vodoraven pas, podokno za predogled "
"sporočil pa bo zasedalo celoten spodnji del okna. Če ste izbrali možnost "
"<guilabel>Pokaži podokno za predogled sporočil poleg seznama sporočil</"
"guilabel>, bosta seznam map in seznam sporočil zavzemala navpični pas, "
"podokno za predogled sporočil pa bo na desni strani."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1069
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Show folder quick search field</guilabel> to create a small "
"text box at the top of the folder list. When you type something in that box, "
"only the folders whose names match the characters you entered will appear. "
"Clear the box to display all your folders."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Pokaži polje za hitro iskanje mape</guilabel>, da "
"ustvarite majhno besedilno polje na vrhu seznama map. Ko nekaj vnesete v to "
"polje, se prikažejo samo mape, katerih imena se ujemajo z vnesenimi znaki. "
"Počistite polje, da se prikažejo vse mape."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1073
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Show Favorite Folders View</guilabel> section allows you to "
"change how your favorite folders are displayed. <guilabel>As Icons</"
"guilabel> uses a lot of space, so if you have several favorite folders you "
"might try <guilabel>As List</guilabel>. If you do not care about favorite "
"folders you can disable this feature altogether by selecting "
"<guilabel>Never</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Prikaži prikaz priljubljenih map</guilabel> lahko "
"spremenite način prikaza priljubljenih map. <guilabel>Kot ikone</guilabel> "
"porabi veliko prostora, zato lahko, če imate več priljubljenih map, "
"poskusite <guilabel>Kot seznam</guilabel>. Če vas priljubljene mape ne "
"zanimajo, lahko to funkcijo popolnoma onemogočite z izbiro možnosti "
"<guilabel>Nikoli</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1079
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On by default, <guilabel>Folder Tooltips</guilabel> display additional "
"information (total number of messages, unread messages, and storage size) "
"when hovering over a folder with the mouse pointer. Select <guilabel>Never</"
"guilabel> to disable this feature."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto vklopljeno, <guilabel>Orodne vrstice mape</guilabel> prikažejo "
"dodatne informacije (skupno število sporočil, neprebrana sporočila in "
"velikost shrambe), ko s kazalcem miške podrsate nad mapo. Izberite "
"<guilabel>Nikoli</guilabel>, če želite to funkcijo onemogočiti."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Message Preview Pane</guilabel> section you can choose "
"where in relation to the message list you want the message preview pane to "
"appear. Or you can remove it entirely, and use only the full screen reader "
"to view selected messages (press &Enter;)."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Podokno za predogled sporočil</guilabel> lahko "
"izberete, kje glede na seznam sporočil naj se prikaže podokno za predogled "
"sporočil. Lahko pa ga v celoti odstranite in za ogled izbranih sporočil "
"uporabite le bralnik celotnega zaslona (pritisnite &Enter;)."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message List"
msgstr "Seznam sporočil"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1093
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Appearance Message List</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Videz seznama sporočil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1099
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Appearance Message List</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Videz seznama sporočil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Appearance (Message List) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek za videz seznama sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use this dialog to alter the appearance of the Message List pane."
msgstr "S tem pogovornim oknom lahko spremenite videz podokna Seznam sporočil."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select <guilabel>Display tooltips for messages and group headers</"
"guilabel>, you will see a brief summary of each message (or group -- depends "
"on the view mode) when the mouse cursor hovers over a message list item."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete možnost <guilabel>Prikaz orodnih vrstic za sporočila in glave "
"skupin</guilabel>, boste videli kratek povzetek vsakega sporočila (ali "
"skupine - odvisno od načina prikaza), ko se kazalec miške pomakne nad "
"element seznama sporočil."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default Aggregation</guilabel> and <guilabel>Default Theme</"
"guilabel> may be overridden using the <guilabel>Folder Properties</guilabel> "
"dialog for each folder individually. Clicking the <guibutton>Configure</"
"guibutton> button opens a window to customize the pre-configured "
"aggregations / themes; you can create your own schemes that way."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeto združevanje</guilabel> in <guilabel>Privzeto temo</"
"guilabel> lahko prekrijete z uporabo pogovornega okna <guilabel>Lastnosti "
"mape</guilabel> za vsako mapo posebej. S klikom na gumb <guibutton>Nastavi</"
"guibutton> se odpre okno za prilagajanje vnaprej konfiguriranih združevanj/"
"tem; na ta način lahko ustvarite svoje sheme."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Eight aggregation modes and three themes have been pre-configured."
msgstr "Osem načinov združevanja in tri teme je bilo predhodno nastavljeno."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Default aggregation:</guilabel> (drop down list)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Privzeto združevanje:</guilabel> (spustni seznam)"

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activity by Date, Flat"
msgstr "Aktivnosti po dnevih, navaden seznam"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view uses day-by-day groups. Messages are not threaded. So for example, "
"in <quote>Today</quote> you will simply find all the messages that arrived "
"today. The groups are displayed by default in reverse chronological order, "
"and labeled \"Today\", \"Yesterday\", then the preceding five days of the "
"week, followed by mm/dd/yy."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled uporablja skupine po dnevih. Sporočila niso po nitih. Tako boste "
"na primer v polju <quote>Danes</quote> preprosto našli vsa sporočila, ki so "
"prispela danes. Skupine so privzeto prikazane v obratnem kronološkem vrstnem "
"redu in označene z \"Danes\", \"Včeraj\", nato s prejšnjih pet dni v tednu, "
"ki jim sledi mm/dd/ll (mesec/dan/leto)."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activity by Date, Threaded"
msgstr "Dejavnost po datumih, po nitih"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view uses day-by-day groups. Messages are threaded. So for example, in "
"<quote>Today</quote> you will find all the messages that arrived today and "
"all the threads that have been active today. Uses the same grouping as "
"Activity by Date, Flat."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled uporablja skupine po dnevih. Sporočila so po nitih. Tako boste na "
"primer v polju <quote>Danes</quote> našli vsa sporočila, ki so prispela "
"danes, in vse niti, ki so bile danes aktivne. Uporablja enako razvrščanje v "
"skupine kot pri storitvi Dejavnost po datumu, Ploščato."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current Activity, Flat"
msgstr "Trenutna dejavnost, navaden seznam"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view uses smart date range groups. Messages are not threaded. So for "
"example, in <quote>Today</quote> you will simply find all the messages that "
"arrived today. The groups are displayed by default in reverse chronological "
"order: \"Today\", \"Yesterday\", the five preceding days of the week, \"Last "
"Week\", \"Two Weeks Ago\", and then month by month."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled uporablja pametne skupine datumskih območij. Sporočila niso "
"nitkana. Tako boste na primer v polju <quote>Danes</quote> preprosto našli "
"vsa sporočila, ki so prispela danes. Skupine so privzeto prikazane v "
"obratnem kronološkem vrstnem redu: \"Danes\", \"Včeraj\", pet predhodnih dni "
"v tednu, \"Prejšnji teden\", \"Pred dvema tednoma\" in nato po mesecih."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current Activity, Threaded"
msgstr "Trenutna dejavnost, po nitih"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view uses smart date range groups. Messages are threaded. So for "
"example, in <quote>Today</quote> you will find all the messages that arrived "
"today and all the threads that have been active today. Otherwise the same as "
"Current Activity, Flat."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled uporablja pametne skupine datumskih območij. Sporočila so po "
"nitih. Tako boste na primer v polju <quote>Danes</quote> našli vsa "
"sporočila, ki so prispela danes, in vse niti, ki so bile danes aktivne. "
"Sicer enako kot pri trenutni dejavnosti, navaden seznam."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flat Date View"
msgstr "Navaden seznam po datumu"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a plain, old-fashioned list of messages sorted by date. No groups "
"and no threading."
msgstr ""
"To je navaden, staromoden seznam sporočil, razvrščenih po datumu. Brez "
"skupin in niti."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Senders/Receivers, Flat"
msgstr "Pošiljatelji/prejemniki, navaden seznam"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view groups the messages by senders or receivers (depending on the "
"folder type). You may specify senders (or receivers) in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Folders</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Folder Properties</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog (\"View\" tab, <guilabel>Show Column:</"
"guilabel>). Messages are not threaded."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogledu so sporočila razvrščena po pošiljateljih ali prejemnikih "
"(odvisno od vrste mape). Pošiljatelje (ali prejemnike) lahko določite v "
"pogovornem oknu <menuchoice><guimenu>Mape</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lastnosti "
"mape</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (zavihek \"Pogled\", <guilabel>Pokaži "
"stolpec:</guilabel>). Sporočila niso po nitih."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standard Mailing List"
msgstr "Standarden dopisni seznam"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a plain, old-fashioned mailing list view: no groups and heavy "
"threading, ordered by the date each thread began."
msgstr ""
"To je navaden, staromoden pogled na poštni seznam: brez skupin in z veliko "
"nitmi, urejen po datumu začetka vsake niti."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thread Starters"
msgstr "Začetniki niti"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view arranges the messages in threads and then groups the threads by "
"the starting user."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled razvrsti sporočila v niti in jih nato združi po začetnem "
"uporabniku."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1171 configure.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Configure...</guibutton> button"
msgstr "Gumb <guibutton>Nastavi</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a custom aggregation theme, click the <guibutton>Configure...</"
"guibutton> button. Select an existing aggregation similar to the one you "
"want to create, then click <guibutton>Clone Aggregation</guibutton>. If none "
"are similar, click the <guibutton>New Aggregation</guibutton> button. The "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> tab allows you to change the <guilabel>Name:</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Description:</guilabel>. The <guilabel>Groups &amp; "
"Threading</guilabel> tab lets you configure several elements to customize "
"your aggregation."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti temo združevanja po meri, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Nastavi</guibutton>. Izberite obstoječe združevanje, podobno "
"tistemu, ki ga želite ustvariti, in kliknite <guibutton>Kloniraj "
"združevanje</guibutton>. Če ni podobnih, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Novo "
"združevanje</guibutton>. V zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> lahko "
"spremenite <guilabel>Ime:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Opis:</guilabel>. Zavihek "
"<guilabel>Skupine &amp; po nitih</guilabel> omogoča konfiguracijo več "
"elementov za prilagoditev združevanja."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Grouping:</guilabel> lets you select from dates, sender/receiver "
"or none. With the smart options &kmail; will group related emails together."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Združevanje:</guilabel> omogoča izbiro med datumi, pošiljateljem/"
"prejemnikom ali nič. S pametnimi možnostmi bo &kmail; združil povezana e-"
"poštna sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Group expand policy:</guilabel> lets you set whether &kmail; will "
"automatically expand grouped emails, or not."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pravilnik razširjanja skupin:</guilabel> omogoča nastavitev, ali "
"bo &kmail; samodejno razširil e-poštna sporočila v skupinah ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Threading:</guilabel> allows you to decide if &kmail; will include "
"references and subject to determine perfect threading. You may also turn off "
"threading altogether."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Združevanje v niti:</guilabel> vam omogoča, da se odločite, ali bo "
"&kmail; vključeval reference in predmet za določitev popolne niti. "
"Združevanje v niti lahko tudi popolnoma izklopite."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Thread leader:</guilabel> lets you change the leader of the "
"thread: most recent message, or the first one."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Začetek niti:</guilabel> omogoča spreminjanje vodilnega sporočila "
"niti: zadnje sporočilo ali prvo sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Thread expand policy:</guilabel> allows you to change how &kmail; "
"determines whether a thread should be expanded."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Politika razširitve niti:</guilabel> omogoča spreminjanje načina, "
"kako &kmail; določi, ali naj se nit razširi."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab lets you change the <guilabel>Fill "
"view strategy:</guilabel> Choose \"Favor speed\" if you have a slow "
"connection. \"Interactivity\" will show all of your current conversations "
"first. \"Batch\" mode will not do any sorting."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> lahko spremenite "
"<guilabel>Strategijo prikaza zapolnitve:</guilabel> Če imate počasno "
"povezavo, izberite \"Daj prednosti hitrosti\". \"Interaktivnost\" bo najprej "
"prikazala vse vaše trenutne pogovore. V načinu \"Paketno\" ne bo razvrščanja."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Default Theme:</guilabel> (drop down list)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Privzeta tema:</guilabel> (spustni seznam)"

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Classic"
msgstr "Klasika"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid "A simple, backward compatible, single row theme"
msgstr "Enostavna, nazaj združljiva tema z eno vrstico"

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smart"
msgstr "Pametno"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1231
#, no-c-format
msgid "A smart multi-line and multi-item theme"
msgstr "Pametna tema z več vrsticami in več postavkami"

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smart with Clickable Status"
msgstr "Pametno s statusom, ki ga je mogoče klikniti"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1235
#, no-c-format
msgid "A smart multi-line and multi-item theme with a clickable status column"
msgstr ""
"Pametna tema z več vrsticami in več postavkami s stolpcem stanja, ki ga je "
"mogoče klikniti"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a custom message list theme, click the <guibutton>Configure...</"
"guibutton> button. Select an existing theme similar to the one you want to "
"create, then click <guibutton>Clone Theme</guibutton>. If none are similar, "
"click the <guibutton>New Theme</guibutton> button. The <guilabel> General</"
"guilabel> tab allows you to change the <guilabel>Name:</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Description:</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti temo seznama sporočil po meri, kliknite "
"<guibutton>Nastavi</guibutton>. Izberite obstoječo temo, podobno tisti, ki "
"jo želite ustvarite, nato kliknite <guibutton>Kloniranje teme</guibutton>. "
"Če nobena ni podobna, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Nova tema</guibutton>. "
"<guilabel> Splošno</guilabel> vam omogoča, da spremenite <guilabel>Ime:</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Opis:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> tab lets you configure visible columns "
"and status items. To add a column, right click the column bar and select "
"<guilabel>Add Column</guilabel>. Name the column, then select what the "
"column will represent from the <guilabel>Header click sorts messages:</"
"guilabel> drop down list. <guilabel>Visible by default</guilabel> is "
"automatically checked. Uncheck it if you only want the column to be "
"available on the context menu for the clickable sort bar. Drag the "
"appropriate label from the <guilabel>Content Items</guilabel> to the column "
"view box under the column bar, &eg;, if you chose to add a size column you "
"would drag the Size label underneath the Size column. Continue to do this "
"until you have all the columns you desire. You can change the font and color "
"of column items through the view area &RMB; menu. Move, delete and resize "
"columns via the &RMB; menu on the column bar."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Videz</guilabel> omogoča konfiguracijo vidnih stolpcev in "
"statusne elemente. Če želite dodati stolpec, z desno tipko miške kliknite "
"vrstico stolpcev in izberite <guilabel>Dodaj stolpec</guilabel>. Poimenujte "
"stolpec, nato izberite, kaj bostolpec predstavljal iz <guilabel>Klik na "
"naslov razvrsti sporočila:</guilabel> spustni seznam. <guilabel>Privzeto "
"vidno</guilabel> je samodejno odkljukano. Odkljukajte ga, če želite, da je "
"stolpec na voljo samo v kontekstnem meniju za vrstico za razvrščanje, na "
"katero lahko kliknete. Povlecite ustrezno oznako iz <guilabel>Postavke "
"vsebine</guilabel> v stolpec. &eg; če ste se odločili dodati stolpec "
"velikosti, ki ga želite prikazati pod vrstico stolpcev, povlecite oznako "
"Velikost pod stolpec Velikost. Nadaljujte s tem dokler nimate vseh želenih "
"stolpcev. Spremenite lahko pisavo in barvo elementov stolpca prek menija "
"območja pogleda &RMB;. Premikanje, brisanje in spreminjanje velikosti "
"stolpcev poteka prek menija &RMB; v vrstici stolpcev."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab lets you show headers. You may also "
"change the size of status icons."
msgstr ""
"Z zavihkom <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> lahko prikažete glave. Spremenite "
"lahko tudi velikost ikon stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Date Display</guilabel> section you may choose one of three "
"date formats (or create your own). The <guilabel>Standard Format</guilabel> "
"shows the day of the week and the date. The <guilabel>Localized Format</"
"guilabel> is shorter, omitting the day of the week. The <guilabel>Smart "
"format</guilabel> will show today, yesterday, &etc; If you want to create a "
"<guilabel>Custom</guilabel> date format, just click on <guilabel>Custom "
"format information</guilabel> and follow the directions."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Prikaz datuma</guilabel> lahko izberete eno od treh "
"oblik datuma (ali ustvarite svojo). <guilabel>Standardni format</guilabel> "
"prikazuje dan v tednu in datum. <guilabel>Mestni format</guilabel> je krajši "
"in ne vsebuje dneva v tednu. <guilabel>Pametni format</guilabel> bo prikazal "
"danes, včeraj in podobno; Če želite ustvariti format datuma <guilabel>Po "
"meri</guilabel>, kliknite <guilabel>Informacije o formatu po meri</guilabel> "
"in sledite navodilom."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Tags"
msgstr "Oznake sporočil"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Appearance Tags</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Videz oznak</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Appearance Tags</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Videz oznak</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1299
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Appearance (Tags) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek za videz (oznak)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; by default gives you several ways to mark messages (Important / "
"Action Item / Birthday), accessible via the <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Mark Message &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice> sub-menu. "
"You may also define additional tags to help you categorize messages."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; privzeto omogoča več načinov označevanja sporočil (Pomembno / "
"Opravilo / Rojstni dan), ki so dostopni prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Označi sporočilo &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice> "
"podmeni. Določite lahko tudi dodatne oznake za lažje razvrščanje sporočil."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Available Tags</guilabel> input field to name your special "
"tag. Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> button to add this "
"name to the list. Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> button "
"to remove a tag. (The \"Birthday\" tag is built-in, and cannot be removed.) "
"Use the up and down arrow buttons to sort the items in the list."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite vnosno polje <guilabel>Dostopne oznake</guilabel>, da poimenujete "
"svojo posebno oznako. Z gumbom <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"dodajte to ime na seznam. Gumb <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"uporabite za odstranitev oznake. (Oznaka \"Rojstni dan\" je vgrajena in je "
"ni mogoče odstraniti.) Za razvrščanje elementov na seznamu uporabite gumba s "
"puščico navzgor in navzdol."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Highlight an item in the list to activate the <guilabel>Tag Settings</"
"guilabel> dialog. You may choose any or all of six options."
msgstr ""
"Označite element na seznamu, da aktivirate pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Nastavitve oznak</guilabel>. Izberete lahko katerokoli od šestih "
"možnosti ali vse."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change text color:"
msgstr "Spremeni barvo besedila:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to display tagged message list entries in a different "
"color. A color palette will be presented when you choose this option. Select "
"a preset color, or choose \"Custom...\" for more flexibility."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite vnose s seznama označenih sporočil prikazati "
"v drugačni barvi. Ko izberete to možnost, se prikaže barvna paleta. Izberite "
"prednastavljeno barvo ali izberite \"Po meri...\" za večjo prilagodljivost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change background color:"
msgstr "Spremeni barvo ozadja:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose this option to alter the background color of tagged message list "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite spremeniti barvo ozadja označenih vnosov "
"seznama sporočil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change font:"
msgstr "Spremeni pisavo:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1335
#, no-c-format
msgid "You may select either a bold or <emphasis>italic</emphasis> type face."
msgstr "Izberete lahko krepko ali <emphasis>ležeče</emphasis> pisavo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message tag icon:"
msgstr "Ikona oznak sporočil:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to open an icon selection dialog. The icon will be "
"displayed on tagged message list entries."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ta gumb, da odprete pogovorno okno za izbiro ikone. Ikona bo "
"prikazana na označenih vnosih seznama sporočil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut:"
msgstr "Bližnjica:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this button to create a keyboard shortcut for associating this tag with "
"selected messages."
msgstr ""
"S tem gumbom ustvarite bližnjico na tipkovnici za povezovanje te oznake z "
"izbranimi sporočili."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable toolbar button:"
msgstr "Omogoči gumb orodne vrstice:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add a new button to the &kmail; toolbar. Clicking the "
"button will tag the currently selected message."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite dodati nov gumb v orodno vrstico &kmail;. S "
"klikom na gumb označite trenutno izbrano sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All the tags defined here will automatically appear as new options in the "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Mark Message &gt;</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> sub-menu."
msgstr ""
"Vse tukaj opredeljene oznake se samodejno prikažejo kot nove možnosti v "
"podmeniju <menuchoice> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Oznake "
"sporočila &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Composer Page"
msgstr "Stran skladatelja"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a description of how to use the <guilabel>Composer</guilabel>, read "
"<link linkend=\"the-composer-window\">this page</link>. To learn more about "
"fine-tuning the <guilabel>Composer</guilabel>'s behavior, press on."
msgstr ""
"Za opis uporabe <guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel>-ja preberite <link linkend="
"\"the-composer-window\">to stran</link>. Če želite izvedeti več o natančnem "
"prilagajanju obnašanja <guilabel>Skladatel</guilabel>-ja, pritisnite."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer General</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Splošno za skladetelja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer General</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Splošno za skladatelja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1391
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer (General) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek (splošno) za skladatelja"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog lets you adjust the way &kmail; handles signatures. It also "
"permits you to control some formatting features, to adjust some "
"autocompletion options, and to tweak &kmail;'s autosave feature."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko prilagodite način, kako &kmail; obdeluje "
"podpise. Omogoča tudi nadzor nekaterih funkcij oblikovanja, prilagoditev "
"nekaterih možnosti samodejnega dopolnjevanja in prilagoditev funkcije "
"samodejnega shranjevanja v e-pošti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically insert signature"
msgstr "Samodejno vstavi podpis"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, your signature as defined on the <link linkend=\"configure-"
"identity-signature\">identity page</link> is automatically included at the "
"end of every message you create (&ie;, new messages, replies, &etc;)."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, se vaš podpis, kot je določen na <link linkend=\"configure-"
"identity-signature\">strani identitet</link>, samodejno vključi na konec "
"vsakega ustvarjenega sporočila (&ie;, nova sporočila, odgovori, &etc;)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert signature above quoted text"
msgstr "Vstavi podpis nad citirano besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will insert your signature at the top of the composer "
"window, and not at the bottom."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; vaš podpis vstavil na vrh okna "
"skladatelja in ne na dno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1430
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prepend separator to signature"
msgstr "Pred podpis dodaj ločilnik"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will insert \"-- \" (dash dash space) before your "
"signature if your signature does not begin that way. (This separator line is "
"a <emphasis>de facto</emphasis> internet standard.)"
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; , če se vaš podpis ne začne na ta "
"način, pred njega vstavil \"-- \" (pomišljaj, pomišljaj, presledek). (Ta "
"ločilna vrstica je <emphasis>de facto</emphasis> internetni standard.)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove the signature when replying"
msgstr "Ob odgovarjanju odstrani podpis"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will remove the signature from the original message when "
"you compose a reply. Of course, if you have not selected the signature and "
"the <guilabel>Only quote selected text ...</guilabel> option has been "
"checked, &kmail; will omit the signature without referring to this setting."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; pri sestavljanju odgovora odstranil "
"podpis iz prvotnega sporočila. Seveda, če podpisa niste izbrali in je bila "
"označena možnost <guilabel>Citiraj samo izbrano besedilo ...</guilabel>, bo "
"&kmail; izpustil podpis, ne da bi se skliceval na to nastavitev."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only quote selected text when replying"
msgstr "Izbrano besedilo citiraj zgolj ob odgovarjanju"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will quote only the selected text in the message window, "
"instead of the complete message, when replying. With this, it is possible to "
"quickly generate replies that quote only the relevant paragraph(s) to which "
"you are actually replying. If this option is checked and you select nothing, "
"&kmail; will quote the entire message."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo &kmail; pri odgovarjanju citiral samo izbrano besedilo v "
"oknu sporočila in ne celotnega sporočila. S tem je mogoče hitro ustvariti "
"odgovore, v katerih so navedeni samo ustrezni odstavki, na katere dejansko "
"odgovarjate. Če je ta možnost označena in ne izberete ničesar, bo &kmail; "
"citiral celotno sporočilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use smart quoting"
msgstr "Uporabljaj pametno citiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will break long lines but will try to keep the correct "
"quoting (&ie;, the <quote>&gt;</quote> will always be at the start of the "
"line)."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost odkljukana, bo &kmail; prekinil dolge vrstice, vendar bo "
"poskušal ohraniti pravilno citiranje (&ie;, <quote>&gt;</quote> bo vedno na "
"začetku vrstice)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1483
#, no-c-format
msgid "Word wrap at column:"
msgstr "Prelom vrstice znotraj besed:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, the word wrap option (<menuchoice> <guimenu>Options</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Wordwrap</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the composer "
"window) will be selected automatically. Use the spin box to set the maximum "
"line length."
msgstr ""
"Če je označena, se samodejno izbere možnost preloma vrstice znotraj besed "
"(<menuchoice> <guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prelom vrstice</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v oknu skladatelja). S poljem za vrtenje "
"nastavite največjo dolžino vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reply or forward using the same visual format as the original message (plain "
"text or HTML)"
msgstr ""
"Odgovorite ali posredujete naprej v isti vizualni obliki kot izvirno "
"sporočilo (navadno besedilo ali HTML)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will always enable the rich text editing toolbar if the "
"message to which you are responding contains an &HTML; &MIME; header. If "
"this option is not selected, the composer retains the toolbar state from the "
"previous session."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; vedno omogočil orodno vrstico za "
"urejanje bogatega besedila, če sporočilo, na katerega odgovarjate, vsebuje "
"glavo &HTML; &MIME;. Če ta možnost ni izbrana, skladatelj ohrani stanje "
"orodne vrstice iz prejšnje seje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Improve plain text version of &HTML; message"
msgstr "Izboljšanje običajne besedilne različice sporočila &HTML;"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will append footnotes to the plain text version of every "
"message composed in &HTML;. These plain text footnotes will be clickable "
"links pointing to any resources coded as anchor tags (aka links) in the "
"&HTML; version of the message."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; vsakemu sporočilu, napisanemu v jeziku "
"&HTML;, dodal opombe pod črto. Te opombe v navadnem besedilu bodo povezave, "
"ki jih je mogoče klikniti in kažejo na vire, ki so v različici sporočila v "
"jeziku &HTML; kodirani kot sidrne oznake (t. i. povezave)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1522
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically request message disposition notifications"
msgstr "Samodejno zahtevajte obvestila o razporeditvi sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, <xref linkend=\"composer-options-request-mdn\"/> will default to "
"<emphasis>on</emphasis>. Check this option only if you know what you are "
"doing. &mdn;s are considered a nuisance (or are simply ignored) by a lot of "
"people. It is better to request them only when necessary."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo možnost <xref linkend=\"composer-options-request-mdn\"/> "
"privzeto <emphasis>vključena</emphasis>. To možnost označite le, če veste, "
"kaj počnete. Številni ljudje menijo, da so obvestila moteča (ali pa jih "
"preprosto ignorirajo). Bolje je, da jih zahtevate le, kadar je to potrebno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use addresses indexed from emails for autocompletion"
msgstr ""
"Za samodejno dokončanje uporabite naslove, indeksirane iz e-poštnih sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will include the addresses from all your saved messages "
"in the list of autocompletion targets (&eg;, when you start typing in the "
"To: input field). These will appear as \"Contacts found in your data\". If "
"you switch this off, only the matching &kaddressbook; entries and \"Recent "
"Addresses\" will appear in the list. Use the spin box to limit the number of "
"items displayed in the list."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; na seznam ciljev za samodejno "
"dokončanje (&eg;, ko začnete pisati v vnosno polje Za:) vključil naslove iz "
"vseh shranjenih sporočil. Ti bodo prikazani kot \"Stiki, najdeni v vaših "
"podatkih\". Če to izklopite, bodo na seznamu prikazani samo ustrezni vnosi "
"&kaddressbook; in \"Zadnji naslovi\". S poljem za vrtenje omejite število "
"prikazanih elementov na seznamu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use recent addresses for autocompletion"
msgstr "Uporaba zadnjih naslovov za samodejno dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will include the addresses that have been used recently "
"in the list of autocompletion targets (&eg;, when you start typing in the "
"CC: input field). These will appear as \"Recent Addresses\". If you switch "
"this off, only the matching &kaddressbook; entries and \"Contacts found in "
"your data\" will appear in the list. Use the spin box to limit the number of "
"items considered \"Recent\"."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; na seznam ciljev samodejnega "
"dokončanja (&eg;, ko začnete pisati v vnosno polje CC:) vključil naslove, ki "
"so bili nedavno uporabljeni. Ti bodo prikazani kot \"Nedavni naslovi\". Če "
"to izklopite, bodo na seznamu prikazani samo ustrezni vnosi &kaddressbook; "
"in \"Stiki, najdeni v vaših podatkih\". S poljem za vrtenje omejite število "
"elementov, ki se štejejo za \"Nedavne\"."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1566
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Configure Completion ...</guibutton> button"
msgstr "Gumb za <guibutton>Nastavi dopolnjevanje...</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on this button to open the autocompletion configuration dialog. You "
"may adjust the order in which items appear, add or remove \"Recent\" "
"addresses, and create a blacklist of addresses that should never appear as "
"autocompletion targets. Notice that this dialog may also be invoked from a "
"context menu by clicking the &RMB; in, say, the \"To:\" field of the "
"composer."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na ta gumb odprete pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo samodejnega "
"dopolnjevanja. Prilagodite lahko vrstni red prikazovanja elementov, dodate "
"ali odstranite naslove \"Nedavni\" in ustvarite črni seznam naslovov, ki se "
"nikoli ne smejo prikazati kot cilji samodejnega dopolnjevanja. Upoštevajte, "
"da lahko to pogovorno okno prikličete tudi iz kontekstnega menija s klikom "
"na &RMB; na primer v polju \"Za:\" sestavljavca."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1582
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autosave interval"
msgstr "Interval samodejnega shranjevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A backup copy of the text in the composer window is by default created "
"regularly. This option lets you specify how often a backup copy is created. "
"You can disable autosaving by selecting \"No autosave\"."
msgstr ""
"Varnostna kopija besedila v oknu skladatelja se privzeto redno ustvarja. S "
"to možnostjo lahko določite, kako pogosto se ustvari varnostna kopija. "
"Samodejno shranjevanje lahko onemogočite tako, da izberete \"Brez "
"samodejnega shranjevanja\"."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standard Templates"
msgstr "Standardne predloge"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1599
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer Standard Templates</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skladatelj standardnih predlog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1605
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer Standard Templates</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skladatelj standardnih predlog</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1608
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer (Standard Templates) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek skladatelja (standarnih predlog)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1614
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can edit the default message templates used when you compose a new "
"message, write a reply, or forward a message. Message templates support "
"substitution commands, by simply typing them or selecting them from the "
"<guimenu>Insert Command</guimenu> menu. These are global (default) "
"templates. They may be overridden by per-identity templates or per-folder "
"templates if any such are specified. Most people are happy with the standard "
"default templates. But if you wish to tweak the defaults, this is the place "
"to do it."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko urejate privzete predloge sporočil, ki se uporabljajo pri "
"sestavljanju novega sporočila, pisanju odgovora ali posredovanju sporočila. "
"Predloge sporočil podpirajo ukaze za zamenjavo, tako da jih preprosto "
"vnesete ali izberete v meniju <guimenu>Vstavi ukaz</guimenu>. To so globalne "
"(privzete) predloge. Nadomeščajo jih lahko predloge na identiteto ali "
"predloge na mapo, če so te določene. Večina ljudi je zadovoljna s "
"standardnimi privzetimi predlogami. Če želite prilagoditi privzete "
"nastavitve, je to pravo mesto za to."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a more detailed explanation of template configuration, please refer to "
"<link linkend=\"configure-identity-templates\">the Identities chapter.</link>"
msgstr ""
"Podrobnejšo razlago konfiguracije predlog najdete v <link linkend="
"\"configure-identity-templates\">poglavju Identitete.</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1632
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Templates"
msgstr "Predloge po meri"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1634
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer Custom Templates</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skladatelj predlog po meri</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1640
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer Custom Templates</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skladatelj predlog po meri</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1643
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer (Custom Templates) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek skladatelja (predlog po meri)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can add, edit, and delete custom message templates to use when you "
"compose a reply or forward a message. Create the custom template by typing "
"the name into the input box and press the <guiicon>+</guiicon> button. You "
"can bind a keyboard combination to the template for faster operations."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko dodajate, urejate in brišete predloge sporočil po meri, ki jih "
"uporabite pri sestavljanju odgovora ali posredovanju sporočila. Predlogo po "
"meri ustvarite tako, da v vnosno polje vnesete ime in pritisnete gumb "
"<guiicon>+</guiicon>. Za hitrejše delovanje lahko na predlogo vežete "
"kombinacijo tipkovnice."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Message templates support substitution commands, by simply typing them or "
"selecting them from the <guimenu>Insert Command</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Predloge sporočil podpirajo ukaze za zamenjavo, tako da jih preprosto "
"vnesete ali izberete v meniju <guimenu>Vestavi ukaz</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are four types of custom templates: used to <guilabel>Reply</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Reply to All</guilabel>, <guilabel>Forward</guilabel>, "
"and <guilabel>Universal</guilabel> which can be used for all kinds of "
"operations. You cannot bind a keyboard shortcut to <guilabel>Universal</"
"guilabel> templates."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo štiri vrste predlog po meri: uporabljajo se za <guilabel>Odgovor</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Odgovor vsem</guilabel>, <guilabel>Naprej</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Univerzalno</guilabel>, ki jih lahko uporabite za vse vrste "
"operacij. Bližnjice tipkovnice ne morete vezati na predloge iz kategorije "
"<guilabel>Univerzalno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1674
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subject"
msgstr "Zadeva"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1676
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer Subject</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skladatelj zadeve</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1682
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer Subject</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skladatelj zadeve</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1685
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer (Subject) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek skladatelja (zadeve)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section contains a list of prefixes for <quote>Reply</quote> and "
"<quote>Forward</quote>. If you receive messages that use prefixes differing "
"from the standard prefixes, you may add them to this list so &kmail; will "
"recognize them. &kmail; will then ignore the odd-ball prefixes when sorting "
"messages (and when setting the subject of a reply or a forwarded message), "
"and optionally replace them with <quote>Re:</quote> or <quote>Fwd:</quote>, "
"respectively."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vsebuje seznam predpon za <quote>Odgovori</quote> in "
"<quote>Posreduj</quote>. Če prejmete sporočila, ki uporabljajo predpone, ki "
"se razlikujejo od standardnih, jih lahko dodate na ta seznam, da jih bo "
"&kmail; prepoznal. &kmail; bo nato pri razvrščanju sporočil (in pri "
"določanju predmeta odgovora ali posredovanega sporočila) prezrl čudne "
"predpone in jih po želji nadomestil z <quote>Odg:</quote> oziroma "
"<quote>Posr:</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1704
#, no-c-format
msgid "Character Set"
msgstr "Nabor znakov"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1706
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer Character Set</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skladatelj nabora znakov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1712
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer Character Set</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skladatelj nabora znakov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1715
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer (Character Set) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek skladatelja (nabora znakov)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can manage the default character sets used for your own messages. "
"Every message you send will be checked to see if it is written with one of "
"the listed character sets, starting at the top of the list. If it is, that "
"character set will be used. If it is not, a dialog will appear and tell you "
"that you must choose a character set via <menuchoice><guimenu>Options</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Set Encoding</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko upravljate privzete nabore znakov, ki se uporabljajo za vaša "
"sporočila. Pri vsakem poslanem sporočilu bo preverjeno, ali je napisano z "
"enim od naštetih naborov znakov, začenši z vrhom seznama. Če je, bo "
"uporabljen ta nabor znakov. Če ni, se prikaže pogovorno okno, v katerem "
"morate izbrati nabor znakov prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Možnosti</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi kodiranje</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select <guilabel>Keep original charset when replying or forwarding "
"(if possible)</guilabel>, the original message's character set will be kept, "
"unless there are now characters that cannot be represented using that set of "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete možnost <guilabel>Ob odgovarjanju in prepošiljanju obdži začeten "
"nabor znakov (če je mogoče)</guilabel>, bo ohranjen nabor znakov izvornega "
"sporočila, razen če so zdaj prisotni znaki, ki jih ni mogoče predstaviti s "
"tem naborom znakov."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1740
#, no-c-format
msgid "Headers"
msgstr "Glave"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1742
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer Headers</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skladatelj glav</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1748
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer Headers</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skladatelj glav</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1751
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer (Headers) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek skladatelja glav"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the <guilabel>Use custom message-id suffix</guilabel> checkbox if you "
"want &kmail; to generate Message-Id's with a custom suffix. Enter the "
"desired suffix in the <guilabel>Custom message-id suffix</guilabel> field. "
"Please make sure that the suffix you specify is unique (within the "
"webiverse). The simplest way to ensure uniqueness is to use the name of your "
"own domain, if you have one. If you do not check <guilabel>Use custom "
"Message-Id suffix</guilabel>, &kmail; will automatically generate the "
"complete Message-Id. If you do not know what this is all about, do not "
"choose this option."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje <guilabel>Uporabi pripono Message-ID po meri</"
"guilabel>, če želite, da &kmail; ustvari Message-ID s končnico po meri. V "
"polje <guilabel>Pripona Message-ID po meri</guilabel> vnesite želeno "
"končnico. Prepričajte se, da je končnica, ki jo določite, edinstvena "
"(znotraj spletne univerze). Najpreprostejši način zagotavljanja "
"edinstvenosti je uporaba imena lastne domene, če jo imate. Če ne potrdite "
"možnosti <guilabel>Use custom Message-Id suffix</guilabel>, bo &kmail; "
"samodejno ustvaril celoten Message-ID. Če ne veste, za kaj gre, ne izberite "
"te možnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Define custom mime header fields</guilabel> list sets the "
"headers that &kmail; will use for its outgoing messages. You may both invent "
"new fields and overwrite existing ones. This feature is only useful for "
"experts."
msgstr ""
"Seznam <guilabel>Definiraj polja mime glav po meri</guilabel> določa glave, "
"ki jih bo &kmail; uporabil za izhodna sporočila. Izumite lahko nova polja in "
"prepišite obstoječa. Ta funkcija je uporabna le za strokovnjake."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1779
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attachments"
msgstr "Priponke"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1781
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer Attachments</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skladatelj priponk</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1787
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer Attachments</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skladatelj priponk</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1790
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer (Attachments) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek skladatelja priponk"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1796
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have to send attachments with filenames containing non-English "
"characters to users of <application>&Microsoft; Outlook</application> or "
"<application>&Microsoft; Outlook Express</application>, you might want to "
"check the <guilabel>Outlook-compatible attachment naming</guilabel> option. "
"&kmail; will then encode the attachment names in a non-standard way that is "
"understood by <application>&Microsoft; Outlook</application>."
msgstr ""
"Če morate priponke z imeni datotek, ki vsebujejo neangleške znake, poslati "
"uporabnikom programov <application>&Microsoft; Outlook</application> ali "
"<application>&Microsoft; Outlook Express</application>, boste morda želeli "
"preveriti možnost <guilabel>Outlook-compatible attachment naming</guilabel>. "
"&kmail; bo nato kodiral imena priponk na nestandardni način, ki ga razume "
"<application>&Microsoft; Outlook</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1806
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select this option, &kmail; will create messages that do not comply "
"with email standards, and consequently it is possible that your messages "
"will not be understood by standards-compliant mail clients. So you should "
"not enable this option unless you must."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, bo &kmail; ustvaril sporočila, ki niso v skladu s "
"standardi e-pošte, zato je mogoče, da vaših sporočil ne bodo razumeli poštni "
"odjemalci, ki so skladni s standardi. Zato te možnosti ne smete omogočiti, "
"razen če je to nujno."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the <guilabel>Enable detection of missing attachments</guilabel> "
"checkbox if you want &kmail; to warn you whenever you are about to send a "
"message without attachments even though the message text contains certain "
"words which may indicate that you want to include an attachment. The list of "
"key words can be modified."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje <guilabel>Omogoči zaznavanje manjkajočih priponk</"
"guilabel>, če želite, da vas &kmail; opozori, kadar koli nameravate poslati "
"sporočilo brez priponk, čeprav besedilo sporočila vsebuje določene besede, "
"ki lahko kažejo, da želite vključiti priponko. Seznam ključnih besed lahko "
"spremenite."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Maximum Attachment Size:</guilabel> spin box to limit the "
"size of any attachments you send. If you try to attach a file larger than "
"the specified limit, &kmail; will issue an error message and refuse to "
"attach the file. Note that this is an individual limit, and not an aggregate "
"limit. Also, the file size is checked before the file is converted to base "
"64 encoding, if that is necessary."
msgstr ""
"S pomočjo vrtilnega polja <guilabel>Maksimalna vellikost priponke:</"
"guilabel> omejite velikost vseh poslanih priponk. Če poskušate pripeti "
"datoteko, ki je večja od te omejitve, bo &kmail; izdal sporočilo o napaki in "
"zavrnil pripenjanje datoteke. Upoštevajte, da je to individualna in ne "
"skupna omejitev. Če je to potrebno, se pred pretvorbo datoteke v kodiranje "
"base 64 preveri tudi velikost datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1833
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Autocorrection</title>"
msgstr "<title>Samodejno popravljanje</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1835
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer Autocorrection</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skladatelj samodejnega popravljanja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1841
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer Autocorrection</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skladatelj samodejnega popravljanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1844
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer (Autocorrection) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek skladatelja (samodejnega popravljanja)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1850
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable automatic correction of common typing errors, select the "
"<guilabel>Enable autocorrection</guilabel> option. Use the drop down list to "
"choose your language. You may import settings, either from "
"<application>LibreOffice</application> or another &kmail; / &calligra; "
"installation, via the <guibutton>Import ... <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guibutton> button. If you need to save "
"your settings for another installation or application, use the "
"<guibutton>Export...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti samodejno popravljanje pogostih napak pri tipkanju, "
"izberite možnost <guilabel>Omogoči samodejno popravljanje</guilabel>. S "
"spustnim seznamom izberite jezik. Nastavitve lahko uvozite iz "
"<application>LibreOffice</application> ali druge namestitve &kmail; / "
"&calligra; preko gumba <guibutton>Uvozi ... <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guibutton>. Če želite shraniti nastavitve "
"za drugo namestitev ali aplikacijo, uporabite gumb <guibutton>Izvozi...</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1861
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autocorrect Options"
msgstr "Možnosti samodejnega popravljanja"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1863
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple Autocorrection"
msgstr "Preprosto samodejno popravljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1865
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to configure &kmail; to automatically correct various common "
"typographical errors. Check the boxes next to the autocorrection features "
"you want."
msgstr ""
"Tako lahko nastavite &kmail; za samodejno popravljanje različnih pogostih "
"tipkarskih napak. Označite polja ob želenih funkcijah samodejnega "
"popravljanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1872
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Quotes"
msgstr "Citati po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1874
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can replace double or single quotes with “smart” quotes by checking the "
"appropriate box. You can also add a non-breaking space before specific "
"punctuation marks in French text by selecting that option."
msgstr ""
"Dvojne ali enojne narekovaje lahko nadomestite s \"pametnimi\" narekovaji "
"tako, da označite ustrezno polje. Z izbiro te možnosti lahko pred določenimi "
"ločili v francoskem besedilu dodate tudi presledek brez preloma."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1881
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Autocorrection"
msgstr "Nadpredno samodejno popravljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can customize automatic word replacement by selecting this option. To "
"enter a custom string that will be replaced automatically, enter the word to "
"be replaced in the <guilabel>Find</guilabel> box and enter the replacement "
"word in the <guilabel>Replace</guilabel> box, then click the <guibutton>Add</"
"guibutton> button. To remove a custom word from the list, highlight that "
"entry and click <guibutton>Remove</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Z izbiro te možnosti lahko prilagodite samodejno zamenjavo besed. Če želite "
"vnesti niz po meri, ki bo samodejno nadomeščen, vnesite besedo, ki jo želite "
"nadomestiti, v polje <guilabel>Poišči</guilabel>, v polje "
"<guilabel>Nadomesti</guilabel> vnesite nadomestno besedo in kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>. Če želite s seznama odstraniti besedo po meri, "
"označite ta vnos in kliknite <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1894
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exceptions"
msgstr "Izjeme"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog lets you create exceptions where you can tell &kmail; to ignore "
"some periods (end of sentence) and two uppercase letters (&eg;, &kmail;). "
"Enter the exception and click the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button. To "
"remove the exception, highlight the string and click <guibutton>Remove</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko ustvarite izjeme, s katerimi lahko naročite, da "
"&kmail; ne upošteva nekaterih pik (konec stavka) in dveh velikih črk (&eg;, "
"&kmail;). Vnesite izjemo in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>. Če "
"želite odstraniti izjemo, označite niz in kliknite <guibutton>Odstrani</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have made all of your autocorrect selections, click "
"<guibutton>Apply</guibutton>, or <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete vse možnosti samodejnega popravljanja, kliknite "
"<guibutton>Uveljavi</guibutton> ali <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:1914
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto Resize Image"
msgstr "Samodejno spremeni velikost slik"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:1916
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer Auto Resize</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skladatelj samodejnega spreminjanja velikosti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:1922
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer Auto Resize</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skladatelj samodejnega spreminjanja velikosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1925
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer (Auto Resize Image) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek skladatelja (samodejnega spreminjanja velikosti slik)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1931
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In some circumstances you may want to have &kmail; automatically resize "
"image attachments in outgoing emails (&eg;, because of server limits). To do "
"so, select <guilabel>Automatically resize images</guilabel>. There are "
"several options that accompany this feature."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih okoliščinah boste morda želeli, da &kmail; samodejno spremeni "
"velikost slikovnih priponk v odhodnih e-poštnih sporočilih (&eg; zaradi "
"omejitev strežnika). Če želite to storiti, izberite <guilabel>Samodejno "
"spreminjanje velikosti slik</guilabel>. Ta funkcija ima več možnosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1938
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>General</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1940
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are three options under \"General\". If you want to preserve the "
"aspect ratio of all images, select <guilabel>Keep ratio</guilabel>. &kmail; "
"by default asks you if you want to resize before resizing. If you want the "
"program to resize images without asking, unselect <guilabel>Ask before "
"resizing</guilabel>. &kmail; will by default send the resized image in "
"<acronym>JPG</acronym> format. If you would rather have such images sent in "
"<acronym>PNG</acronym> format, select that from the <guilabel>Fallback to "
"format:</guilabel> drop down box."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku \"Splošno\" so na voljo tri možnosti. Če želite ohraniti razmerje "
"stranic vseh slik, izberite <guilabel>Ohrani razmerje</guilabel>. &kmail; "
"privzeto vas pred spreminjanjem velikosti vpraša, ali želite spremeniti "
"velikost. Če želite, da program spremeni velikost slik brez vprašanja, "
"odstranite izbiro možnosti <guilabel>Vprašaj pred spremembo velikosti</"
"guilabel>. &kmail; bo privzeto poslal spremenjeno velikost slike v formatu "
"<acronym>JPG</acronym>. Če želite, da se takšne slike pošljejo v formatu "
"<acronym>PNG</acronym>, ga izberite v spustnem polju <guilabel>Zasilna "
"oblika zapisa:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1950
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image"
msgstr "Slika"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Suppose you have a relative who can only receive image files of a certain "
"size because of their email provider's limits. You can use the "
"<guilabel>Reduce image to maximum dimension:</guilabel> option to select a "
"size to shrink the image to, and enter their email into the filters on the "
"<guilabel>Recipients</guilabel> tab. (The <guilabel>Recipients</guilabel> "
"tab is discussed in further detail below.) If you need a custom size, choose "
"the last option <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> from the width and height drop "
"down boxes, and enter a number of pixels in the text box. You may also "
"enlarge images by selecting <guilabel>Enlarge image to minimum dimension</"
"guilabel>. The last option allows you to skip resizing images that are "
"smaller than the specified file size."
msgstr ""
"Recimo, da imate sorodnika, ki zaradi omejitev svojega ponudnika e-pošte "
"lahko prejema le slikovne datoteke določene velikosti. Z možnostjo "
"<guilabel>Zmanjšaj sliko na največjo dimenzijo:</guilabel> lahko izberete "
"velikost, na katero želite zmanjšati sliko, in v filtre na zavihku "
"<guilabel>Prejemniki</guilabel> vnesete njihovo e-pošto. (Zavihek "
"<guilabel>Prejemniki</guilabel> je podrobneje opisan v nadaljevanju.) Če "
"potrebujete velikost po meri, izberite zadnjo možnost <guilabel>Po meri</"
"guilabel> v spustnih poljih za širino in višino ter v besedilno polje "
"vnesite število slikovnih pik. Slike lahko povečate tudi tako, da izberete "
"<guilabel>Povečanj slike na najmanjšo dimenzijo</guilabel>. Zadnja možnost "
"vam omogoča, da preskočite spreminjanje velikosti slik, ki so manjše od "
"določene velikosti datoteke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1965
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filename"
msgstr "Ime datoteke"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1969
#, no-c-format
msgid "Source filter"
msgstr "Filtriranje virov"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1971
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would like the resizing to be done based on the name of the file, "
"select the appropriate filter here. Suppose you need to send your boss "
"multiple images daily, and your boss requires all of them to be the same "
"size. You could name your work images work1, work2 &etc;, then select "
"<guilabel>Include all files whose names contains one of the patterns</"
"guilabel> and enter work into the <guilabel>Pattern:</guilabel> text box. "
"You can also exclude files in the same way by selecting <guilabel>Exclude "
"all files whose names contains one of the patterns</guilabel>. The default "
"behavior is no filtering."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da se velikost spremeni na podlagi imena datoteke, tukaj izberite "
"ustrezen filter. Recimo, da morate svojemu šefu dnevno poslati več slik, ta "
"pa zahteva, da so vse enako velike. Slike iz dela lahko poimenujete delo1, "
"delo2 in tako naprej, nato izberete možnost <guilabel>Vključi vse datoteke, "
"katerih imena vsebujejo enega od vzorcev</guilabel>, in v besedilno polje "
"<guilabel>Vzorec:</guilabel> vnesete delo. Datoteke lahko na enak način "
"izključite tudi tako, da izberete možnost <guilabel>Izključi vse datoteke, "
"katerih imena vsebujejo enega od vzorcev</guilabel>. Privzeto obnašanje je "
"brez filtriranja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1981
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image Format"
msgstr "Format slike"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1983
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Resize all images with one of these formats</guilabel> to "
"set a specific format to resize the image to."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Spremeni velikost vseh slik te vrste</guilabel>, če "
"želite nastaviti določeno obliko, v katero naj se spremeni velikost slike."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this option is enabled, you must click the <guibutton>Select Format...</"
"guibutton> button, then select a format from the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta možnost omogočena, morate klikniti gumb <guibutton>Izberite "
"obliko...</guibutton> in nato v pogovornem oknu izbrati obliko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:1996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resize filename"
msgstr "Spremeni velikost datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Rename resized images with the following pattern:</"
"guilabel> if you would like your resized images to be renamed with a "
"specific pattern. Enter the pattern into the text box. You may use:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Slike po spremembi velikosti preimenuj po naslednjem "
"vzorcu</guilabel>, če želite, da se spremenjene slike preimenujejo z "
"določenim vzorcem. Vzorec vnesite v besedilno polje. Uporabite lahko:"

#. Tag: member
#: configure.docbook:2002
#, no-c-format
msgid "%t set current time"
msgstr "%t nastavi trenutni čas"

#. Tag: member
#: configure.docbook:2003
#, no-c-format
msgid "%d set current date"
msgstr "%d nastavi trenutni datum"

#. Tag: member
#: configure.docbook:2004
#, no-c-format
msgid "%n original filename"
msgstr "%n ime izvorne datoteke"

#. Tag: member
#: configure.docbook:2005
#, no-c-format
msgid "%e original extension"
msgstr "%e izvorna pripona"

#. Tag: member
#: configure.docbook:2006
#, no-c-format
msgid "%x new extension"
msgstr "%x nova pripona"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2016
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recipients"
msgstr "Prejemniki"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab is where you specify recipients who need to receive resized images. "
"You must decide if you need multiple entries or only one, and enter the "
"email(s) into the text box using the <quote>;</quote> as a separator when "
"there are multiple items. You may also specify certain recipients for whom "
"images ought not be resized. The default is no filtering."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku določite prejemnike, ki morajo prejemati slike spremenjene "
"velikosti. Odločiti se morate, ali potrebujete več vnosov ali samo enega, in "
"v besedilno polje vnesti e-poštne naslove, pri čemer uporabite <quote>;</"
"quote> kot ločilo, če je naslovov več. Določite lahko tudi določene "
"prejemnike, za katere se velikost slik ne sme spreminjati. Privzeto je brez "
"filtriranja."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:2034
#, no-c-format
msgid "Security Page"
msgstr "Varnostna stran"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Security configuration dialog lets you fine-tune certain rich text "
"(&HTML;) options. It also allows you to control encryption and decryption "
"features, to adjust some built-in anti-phishing logic, and to specify how "
"message disposition notification requests (aka return receipts) are handled. "
"Notice that this dialog does <emphasis>not</emphasis> have anything to do "
"with anti-virus security measures. See the <link linkend=\"the-anti-virus-"
"wizard\">Using &kmail;: The Anti-Virus Wizard</link> chapter if you want "
"anti-virus security."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu Varnostna konfiguracija lahko natančno nastavite nekatere "
"možnosti bogatega besedila (&HTML;). Omogoča tudi nadzor funkcij šifriranja "
"in dešifriranja, prilagajanje nekaterih vgrajenih logičnih postopkov za "
"preprečevanje ribarjenja in določanje načina obravnave zahtevkov za "
"obvestilo o usodi sporočila (t. i. povratnih potrdil). Upoštevajte, da to "
"pogovorno okno <emphasis>nima nič</emphasis> opraviti z varnostnimi ukrepi "
"protivirusne zaščite. Če želite zagotoviti protivirusno varnost, glejte "
"poglavje <link linkend=\"the-anti-virus-wizard\">Uporaba &kmail;-a: čarovnik "
"za protivirusno zaščito</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:2046
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reading"
msgstr "Branje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:2049
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Security Reading</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Varnost za branje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:2055
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Security Reading</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Varnost za branje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2058
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Security (Reading) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek varnost (za branje)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2064
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this tab you can configure security options that affect the way you read "
"messages."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku lahko nastavite varnostne možnosti, ki vplivajo na način "
"branja sporočil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2069
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prefer HTML to plain text"
msgstr "Prednjači HTML pred navadnim besedilom"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &kmail; will show &HTML; messages in plain text. If you prefer to "
"view messages with &HTML; formatting and layout automatically, select this "
"option. However, we recommend leaving this option off, as security problems "
"with &HTML; might show up."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto bo &kmail; prikazal &HTML; sporočila v navadnem besedilu. Če želite "
"sporočila s &HTML; oblikovanjem in postavitvijo prikazati samodejno, "
"izberite to možnost. Vendar priporočamo, da ta možnost ni vključena, saj se "
"lahko pojavijo varnostne težave z &HTML;."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can still easily view messages in &HTML; format by clicking the plain "
"message/HTML message toggle bar on the left hand side of the preview pane."
msgstr ""
"Sporočila v obliki &HTML; si lahko še vedno preprosto ogledate tako, da "
"kliknete preklopno vrstico navadno sporočilo/sporočilo HTML na levi strani "
"podokna za predogled."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2084
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow messages to load external references from the Internet"
msgstr "Omogočanje sporočil za nalaganje zunanjih referenc iz interneta"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2086
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; can load external images, style sheets, &etc; from the "
"Internet when you view an &HTML; message. We strongly recommend that you "
"leave this option off (although it has no effect until you enable &HTML;)."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, lahko &kmail; ob ogledu sporočila &HTML; naloži "
"zunanje slike, slogovne liste itd. iz interneta. Priporočamo, da to možnost "
"pustite izklopljeno (čeprav nima učinka, dokler ne omogočite &HTML;)."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By adding external references to their messages, people sending spam can "
"detect when you have looked at their message, your location, and a lot of "
"other information that may get logged on web servers. Note that this option "
"has no effect on &Java; or JavaScript, as these are not supported in &kmail; "
"at all."
msgstr ""
"Z dodajanjem zunanjih referenc v svoja sporočila lahko pošiljatelji neželene "
"pošte ugotovijo, kdaj ste si ogledali njihovo sporočilo, vašo lokacijo in "
"številne druge informacije, ki se lahko zabeležijo na spletnih strežnikih. "
"Upoštevajte, da ta možnost ne vpliva na &Java; ali JavaScript, saj v &kmail; "
"sploh nista podprta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Informs if message reading is a suspected email scam"
msgstr "Obvesti, če je prebrano sporočilo domnevna e-poštna goljufija"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As email has become more popular, email scams have proliferated. Email scams "
"may include emails made to appear as if they come from legitimate companies, "
"even though they really link to malicious web sites requesting your personal "
"information. This may lead to identity theft, and worse. By default &kmail; "
"analyzes messages for common scams, and will inform you if a message is a "
"suspected scam. We recommend that you keep this feature enabled. If you wish "
"to disable these warnings, uncheck <guilabel>Informs if message reading is a "
"suspected email scam</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Z vse večjo priljubljenostjo e-pošte so se razširile tudi goljufije po e-"
"pošti. Elektronske prevare lahko vključujejo e-poštna sporočila, ki so "
"videti, kot da prihajajo od zakonitih podjetij, čeprav v resnici vodijo na "
"zlonamerna spletna mesta, ki zahtevajo vaše osebne podatke. To lahko privede "
"do kraje identitete in česa še hujšega. Privzeto &kmail; analizira sporočila "
"za običajne prevare in vas obvesti, če obstaja sum, da gre za prevaro. "
"Priporočamo, da ta funkcija ostane omogočena. Če želite ta opozorila "
"onemogočiti, odstranite potrditev možnosti <guilabel>Obvešča, če se pri "
"branju sporočila sumi, da gre za prevaro e-pošte</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If legitimate emails are being flagged, (&eg;, from trusted friends), you "
"can add their email addresses to the <guilabel>Whitelist:</guilabel> by "
"clicking the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button and entering an address "
"into the dialog that pops up. Please note that at this time, only complete "
"email addresses can be whitelisted."
msgstr ""
"Če so označena legitimna e-poštna sporočila (npr. od zaupanja vrednih "
"prijateljev), lahko njihove e-poštne naslove dodate na <guilabel>Belo listo:"
"</guilabel> tako, da kliknete gumb <guibutton>Dodaj...</guibutton> in v "
"pogovorno okno, ki se prikaže, vnesete naslov. Upoštevajte, da je trenutno "
"mogoče na beli seznam uvrstiti le popolne e-poštne naslove."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check URL with Phishing Google System"
msgstr "Preverite URL z Googlovim sistemom Phishing"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to force &kmail; to consult Google's database of "
"suspected phishing web sites when URLs are embedded in a message, and to "
"warn you whenever a match is found."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite, da &kmail; pri vstavljanju URL-jev v "
"sporočilo poišče Googlovo podatkovno zbirko domnevno goljufivih spletnih "
"mest in vas opozori, ko najde ujemanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scan emails for tracking URLs"
msgstr "Skeniranje e-poštnih sporočil za URL-je za sledenje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, &kmail; will automatically check URLs embedded in &HTML; "
"messages, and warn you if any of them appear to be trying to track you."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto bo &kmail; samodejno preverjal URL-je, vdelane v sporočila &HTML; "
"in vas opozoril, če se bo zdelo, da vas kdo od njih poskuša izslediti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attempt decryption of encrypted messages when viewing"
msgstr "Poskus dešifriranja šifriranih sporočil pri ogledu"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, &kmail; will automatically attempt to decrypt encrypted messages "
"when you view them. If you prefer to do this manually, unselect this option."
msgstr ""
"Po privzetih nastavitvah bo &kmail; samodejno poskušal dešifrirati šifrirana "
"sporočila, ko si jih boste ogledali. Če želite to narediti ročno, te "
"možnosti ne izberite."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically import keys and certificate"
msgstr "Samodejno uvozite ključe in potrdila"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; automatically imports any attachments containing "
"&openpgp; keys into your local keyring, and any attachments containing "
"&smime; keys into your local key box."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, &kmail; samodejno uvozi vse priloge, ki vsebujejo "
"ključe &openpgp;, v vaš lokalni sveženj ključev in vse priloge, ki vsebujejo "
"ključe &smime;, v vaš lokalni predal s ključi."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Verifying &smime; signatures always involves importing the contained "
"certificates. This option does not affect that. It is also unrelated to "
"&gpg;'s <option>auto-key-retrieve</option> feature, where &gpg; will try to "
"import unknown keys from a key server."
msgstr ""
"Preverjanje podpisov &smime; vedno vključuje uvoz vsebovanih potrdil. Ta "
"možnost na to ne vpliva. Prav tako ni povezana s funkcijo <option>auto-"
"pridobivanje-ključev</option> v programu &gpg;, kjer bo program &gpg; "
"poskušal uvoziti neznane ključe iz strežnika ključev."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:2176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Message Disposition Notifications</title>"
msgstr "<title>Obvestila o usodi sporočil</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:2178
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Security MDNs</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Varnost za obvestila o usodi sporočil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:2184
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Security MDNs</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Varnost za obvestila o usodi sporočil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2187
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Security (Message Disposition Notifications) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek varnost (za obvestila o usodi sporočil)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2196
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Message Disposition Notifications</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Obvestila o usodi sporočil</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&mdn;s are a generalization of what is commonly called a <quote>read "
"receipt</quote>. The message author requests a disposition notification to "
"be sent, and the receiver's email program generates a reply from which the "
"author can learn what happened to his message. Common disposition types "
"include <quote>displayed</quote> (&ie;, read), <quote>deleted</quote>, and "
"<quote>dispatched</quote> (&ie;, forwarded)."
msgstr ""
"&mdn;s (obvestila o usodi sporočil) so posplošitev tistega, kar se običajno "
"imenuje <quote>potrdilo o branju</quote>. Avtor sporočila zahteva, da se "
"pošlje obvestilo o razporeditvi, e-poštni program prejemnika pa ustvari "
"odgovor, iz katerega lahko avtor izve, kaj se je zgodilo z njegovim "
"sporočilom. Običajne vrste dispozicij vključujejo <quote>prikazano</quote> "
"(&ie;, branje), <quote>izbrisano</quote> in <quote>poslano</quote> (&ie;, "
"posredovanje)."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following options (listed as <guilabel>Send policy</guilabel>) are "
"available to control <emphasis>when</emphasis> &kmail; sends &mdn;s."
msgstr ""
"Naslednje možnosti (navedene kot <guilabel>Pravilnik pošiljanja</guilabel>) "
"so na voljo za nadzor <emphasis>kdaj</emphasis> &kmail; pošlje &mdn;s "
"(obvestila o usodi sporočil)."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:2216
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Ignore</guilabel> (recommended)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Preziraj</guilabel> (priporočeno)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ignores any request for disposition notifications. No &mdn;s will ever be "
"sent automatically."
msgstr ""
"Ne upošteva nobene zahteve za obvestila o razporeditvi. Nikoli ne bo "
"samodejno poslano nobenega &mdn;s."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2230
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Ask</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Sprašuj</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Answers requests only after asking the user for permission. This way, you "
"can send &mdn;s for selected messages while denying or ignoring them for "
"others."
msgstr ""
"Na zahteve za obvestila odgovori šele po tem, ko uporabnika vpraša za "
"dovoljenje. Tako lahko za izbrana sporočila pošljete &mdn;s, za druga pa jih "
"zavrnete ali ignorirate."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deny"
msgstr "Zavračaj"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Always sends a <quote>denied</quote> notification. This is only "
"<emphasis>slightly</emphasis> better than always sending &mdn;s. The author "
"will still know that the message has been acted upon; he just cannot tell "
"whether it was deleted or read, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Vedno pošlje obvestilo <quote>zavrnjeno</quote>. To je le <emphasis>malo</"
"emphasis> bolje kot vedno pošiljati &mdn;s. Avtor bo še vedno vedel, da je "
"bilo sporočilo uporabljeno, ne bo pa mogel vedeti, ali je bilo izbrisano ali "
"prebrano itd;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always send"
msgstr "Pošljaj vedno"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Always sends the requested disposition notification. This means that the "
"author of the message gets to know when the message was acted upon and, in "
"addition, what happened to it (displayed, deleted, &etc;). This option is "
"strongly discouraged, but since it makes sense where privacy is not a "
"concern, &eg;, in customer relationship management, it has been made "
"available."
msgstr ""
"Vedno pošlje zahtevano obvestilo o razporeditvi. To pomeni, da avtor "
"sporočila izve, kdaj je bilo sporočilo obravnavano in kaj se je z njim "
"zgodilo (prikazano, izbrisano &etc;.). Ta možnost se močno odsvetuje, ker pa "
"je smiselna tam, kjer zasebnost ni pomembna, &eg;. pri upravljanju odnosov s "
"strankami, je dana na voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are unsure, experiment a while with <guilabel>Ask</guilabel>. Then, "
"if you find &kmail;'s questions annoying, switch to <guilabel>Ignore</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če niste prepričani, nekaj časa eksperimentirajte s funkcijo "
"<guilabel>Sprašuj</guilabel>. Če ugotovite, da vas vprašanja &kmail;-a "
"motijo, preklopite na <guilabel>Preziraj</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following options (listed as <guilabel>Quote original message</"
"guilabel>) are available to control <emphasis>how much</emphasis> of the "
"original message &kmail; sends back with &mdn;s."
msgstr ""
"Naslednje možnosti (navedene kot <guilabel>Citiraj izvorno besedilo</"
"guilabel>) so na voljo za nadzor <emphasis>kolikšen del</emphasis> izvornega "
"sporočila &kmail; pošlje nazaj z &mdn;s."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nothing"
msgstr "Nič"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No parts of the message other than the mandatory message-id and the original "
"recipient are included in the &mdn; reply. This preserves enough information "
"for the sender to uniquely identify the message for which this &mdn; was "
"generated."
msgstr ""
"V odgovor &mdn; niso vključeni nobeni deli sporočila razen obveznega message-"
"id in prvotnega prejemnika. Pri tem se ohrani dovolj informacij, da lahko "
"pošiljatelj enolično prepozna sporočilo, za katero je bil ustvarjen ta &mdn;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Full message"
msgstr "Celotno sporočilo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Attaches the complete message to the disposition notification. Usually, this "
"is overkill. It does not add any valuable information that cannot be deduced "
"from the message headers alone, but people sometimes insist on this, since "
"it is much easier for humans to correlate the content of the message (and "
"not just the headers) with what they sent earlier."
msgstr ""
"Obvestilu o razporeditvi priloži celotno sporočilo. Običajno je to "
"pretiravanje. Ne dodaja nobenih dragocenih informacij, ki jih ni mogoče "
"razbrati samo iz glave sporočila, vendar ljudje včasih vztrajajo pri tem, "
"saj ljudje veliko lažje povežejo vsebino sporočila (in ne samo glave) s tem, "
"kar so poslali prej."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only headers"
msgstr "Samo glave"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Attaches only the headers to the disposition notification. This is usually "
"enough to enable both humans (by subject) and computers (by message-id) to "
"easily correlate &mdn; and original message."
msgstr ""
"Obvestilu o razporeditvi priloži samo glave. To je običajno dovolj, da lahko "
"ljudje (po predmetu) in računalniki (po ID sporočila) zlahka povežejo &mdn; "
"in izvirno sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2341
#, no-c-format
msgid "If unsure, leave this option set to the default value (nothing)."
msgstr ""
"Če niste prepričani, pustite to možnost nastavljeno na privzeto vrednost "
"(nič)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2349
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not send MDNs in response to encrypted messages"
msgstr "Ne pošiljajte MDN kot odgovor na šifrirana sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option suppresses the sending of &mdn;s if the message is encrypted "
"(partially or in whole). This thwarts attempts to use &kmail;'s &mdn; "
"feature as an <emphasis>oracle</emphasis> to deduce whether you were able to "
"decrypt the message or not."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost onemogoči pošiljanje simbolov &mdn;, če je sporočilo šifrirano "
"(delno ali v celoti). To preprečuje poskuse uporabe funkcije &mdn; storitve "
"&kmail; kot <emphasis>preroka</emphasis> za sklepanje, ali ste lahko "
"dešifrirali sporočilo ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Strictly speaking, this option is not needed, since &kmail; sends &mdn;s "
"whether the message could be successfully decrypted, or not (the disposition "
"notification request resides in the unencrypted part of the message); but it "
"gives the security-conscious user a choice: either to send them when "
"requested (option unchecked), or never (option checked)."
msgstr ""
"Strogo gledano ta možnost ni potrebna, saj &kmail; pošilja &mdn;s ne glede "
"na to, ali je bilo sporočilo mogoče uspešno dešifrirati ali ne (zahteva za "
"obvestilo o razporeditvi se nahaja v nešifriranem delu sporočila); vendar "
"daje uporabniku, ki se zaveda varnosti, možnost izbire: ali jih bo pošiljal "
"na zahtevo (možnost ni označena) ali nikoli (možnost je označena)."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2368
#, no-c-format
msgid "If unsure, leave this option checked (the default value)."
msgstr "Če niste prepričani, pustite to možnost označeno (privzeta vrednost)."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:2378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Composing"
msgstr "Sestavljanje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:2380
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Security Composing</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Varnost za sestavljanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:2386
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Security Composing</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Varnost za sestavljanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2389
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Security (Composing) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek varnost za sestavljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this tab you can configure security-relevant options for composing "
"messages."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku lahko konfigurirate varnostno pomembne možnosti za "
"sestavljanje sporočil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically sign messages"
msgstr "Samodejno podpisuj sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, the <xref linkend=\"composer-options-sign-message\"/> option in "
"the composer will default to <emphasis>on</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo možnost <xref linkend=\"composer-options-sign-message\"/> "
"v skladatelju privzeta na <emphasis>vključeno</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2412
#, no-c-format
msgid "However, you can still switch it on and off on a per-message basis."
msgstr "Še vedno pa jo lahko vklopite in izklopite za posamezno sporočilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When encrypting emails, always also encrypt to the certificate of my own "
"identity"
msgstr ""
"Pri šifriranju e-poštnih sporočil vedno šifrirajte tudi s potrdilom lastne "
"identitete"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, any message that is encrypted to the recipients will "
"additionally be encrypted to yourself."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo vsako sporočilo, ki je šifrirano za prejemnike, šifrirano "
"tudi za vas."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you uncheck this option, you may not be able to decrypt the messages "
"written by yourself and encrypted to other people any more."
msgstr ""
"Če odkljukate to možnost, morda ne boste mogli več dešifrirati sporočil, ki "
"ste jih napisali sami in so bila šifrirana drugim osebam."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Store sent messages encrypted"
msgstr "Shranjevanje poslanih sporočil v šifrirani obliki"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option enables a mode of using mail encryption that is sometimes "
"(misleadingly) called <quote>transport-only</quote> encryption. In this mode "
"of operation, the message encryption is stripped off as soon as the message "
"has reached its destination. The encryption lasts only while the message is "
"on its way."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost omogoča način šifriranja pošte, ki se včasih (zavajujoče) imenuje "
"<quote>šifriranje samo za prenos</quote>. V tem načinu delovanja se "
"šifriranje sporočila odstrani takoj, ko sporočilo doseže svoj cilj. "
"Šifriranje traja le, dokler je sporočilo na poti."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; supports this mode half-heartedly, since such functionality should "
"be placed at the mail <emphasis>server</emphasis> (<acronym>MTA</acronym>) "
"and not at the mail <emphasis>client</emphasis> (<acronym>MUA</acronym>) "
"level. Thus, future versions of &kmail; may drop support for this option."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; ta način podpira polovično, saj bi morala biti takšna funkcionalnost "
"nameščena na ravni poštnega <emphasis>strežnika</emphasis> (<acronym>MTA</"
"acronym>) in ne na ravni poštnega <emphasis>odjemalca</emphasis> "
"(<acronym>MUA</acronym>). V prihodnjih različicah programa &kmail; bo ta "
"možnost morda opuščena."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, messages are stored in your <guilabel>sent-mail</guilabel> "
"folder just as you sent them (&ie; if they were encrypted, they are also "
"stored that way)."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, so sporočila v mapi <guilabel>poslana-sporočila</guilabel> "
"shranjena tako, kot ste jih poslali (&ie; če so bila šifrirana, so prav tako "
"shranjena na ta način)."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If unchecked, messages will <emphasis>always</emphasis> be stored "
"unencrypted in your <guilabel>sent-mail</guilabel> folder, even if they are "
"sent encrypted."
msgstr ""
"Če potrditev ni označena, bodo sporočila v mapi <guilabel>poslana-sporočila</"
"guilabel> <emphasis>vselej</emphasis> shranjena nešifrirana, tudi če so "
"poslana šifrirano."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always show the encryption keys for approval"
msgstr "Za odobritev vedno pokažite šifrirne ključe"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, every time you encrypt a message, a dialog will appear that "
"presents you with the encryption keys that will be used for each recipient. "
"You may then review the choice of keys, change them, and approve or cancel "
"the encryption operation. We recommend to keep this option checked, since it "
"makes the encryption process more transparent."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, se ob vsakem šifriranju sporočila prikaže pogovorno okno, v "
"katerem so prikazani šifrirni ključi, ki bodo uporabljeni za vsakega "
"prejemnika. Nato lahko pregledate izbiro ključev, jih spremenite ter "
"potrdite ali prekličete šifriranje. Priporočamo, da je ta možnost označena, "
"saj je postopek šifriranja tako bolj pregleden."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2496
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically encrypt messages whenever possible"
msgstr "Samodejno šifriranje sporočil, kadar je to mogoče"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also called <quote>opportunistic encryption</quote>. If checked, &kmail; "
"will try to match recipients to (&openpgp; or &smime;) keys even when you "
"did <emphasis>not</emphasis> specifically request encryption. If usable keys "
"are found for all recipients, &kmail; will ask whether or not you want to "
"encrypt the message."
msgstr ""
"Imenuje se tudi <quote>oportunistično šifriranje</quote>. Če je ta možnost "
"označena, bo &kmail; poskušal ujemati prejemnike s ključi (&openpgp; ali "
"&smime;), tudi če šifriranja <emphasis>ne</emphasis> zahtevate izrecno. Če "
"so za vse prejemnike najdeni uporabni ključi, vas bo &kmail; vprašal, ali "
"želite sporočilo šifrirati ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is highly recommended to turn this on, as it makes encryption really easy "
"to use."
msgstr ""
"Priporočljivo je, da to možnost vklopite, saj je uporaba šifriranja zelo "
"enostavna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2517
#, no-c-format
msgid "Never sign/encrypt when saving as draft"
msgstr "Nikoli ne podpišite/šifrirajte, ko shranjujete kot osnutek"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will not attempt to sign and/or encrypt messages that "
"are merely saved to the <guilabel>drafts</guilabel> folder. This is more "
"convenient, and does not result in a gross loss of security, provided the "
"drafts folder is safe. &IMAP; users might want this option turned off, if "
"their <guilabel>drafts</guilabel> folder is on the server."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, &kmail; ne bo poskušal podpisati in/ali šifrirati "
"sporočil, ki so samo shranjena v mapo <guilabel>osnutki</guilabel>. To je "
"bolj priročno in ne pomeni velike izgube varnosti, če je mapa z osnutki "
"varna. &IMAP; uporabniki bodo morda želeli to možnost izklopiti, če je "
"njihova mapa <guilabel>osnutki</guilabel> v strežniku."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:2537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Razno"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:2539
#, no-c-format
msgid "Security Miscellaneous Autocorrection"
msgstr "Varnost za različne možnosti samodejnega popravljanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:2545
#, no-c-format
msgid "Security Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Različne možnosti samodejnega popravljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2548
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Security (Miscellaneous) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek varnost za različne možnosti samodejnega popravljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2555
#, no-c-format
msgid "On this tab you can switch security-relevant warnings on and off."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku lahko vklopite ali izklopite varnostno pomembna opozorila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2564
#, no-c-format
msgid "Warn when trying to send unsigned messages"
msgstr "Opozori ob poskusu pošiljanja nepodpisanega sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will show a warning if for whatever reason a message "
"would be sent without being digitally signed."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; prikazal opozorilo, če bo sporočilo iz "
"kakršnegakoli razloga poslano, ne da bi bilo digitalno podpisano."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Warn when trying to send unencrypted messages"
msgstr "Opozorilo ob poskusu pošiljanja nešifriranih sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will show a warning if for whatever reason a message "
"would be sent without being encrypted."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; prikazal opozorilo, če bi sporočilo iz "
"kakršnegakoli razloga bilo poslano, ne da bi bilo šifrirano."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While it is common to sign all outgoing messages, encrypting them is not. So "
"unless your company has a policy of never sending any unencrypted messages, "
"it might be a good idea to keep this option switched off and rely on <link "
"linkend=\"configure-security-composing-opportunistic-encryption"
"\">opportunistic encryption</link> to alert you if you <emphasis>could</"
"emphasis> send encrypted messages, but did not request it."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je podpisovanje vseh odhodnih sporočil običajno, pa njihovo "
"šifriranje ni. Če torej vaše podjetje nima politike, da nikoli ne sme "
"pošiljati nešifriranih sporočil, je morda dobro, da je ta možnost "
"izklopljena in se zanašate na <link linkend=\"configure-security-composing-"
"opportunistic-encryption\">oportunistično šifriranje</link>, ki vas opozori, "
"če <emphasis>bi lahko</emphasis> poslali šifrirana sporočila, vendar tega "
"niste zahtevali."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Warn if certificates/keys expire soon"
msgstr "Opozori, če certifikatom/ključem kmalu poteče veljavnost"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kmail; will warn when an &smime; certificate or &openpgp; key "
"is used which will expire soon."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &kmail; opozoril, če se uporabljate potrdilo "
"&smime; ali ključ &openpgp;, ki bo kmalu potekel."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The period in which to warn before key/certificate expiration can then be "
"configured separately for signing and encryption keys, as well as (in the "
"case of &smime;), for end-user certificates, intermediate <acronym>CA</"
"acronym> certificates and root certificates."
msgstr ""
"Obdobje, v katerem je treba opozoriti pred iztekom veljavnosti ključa/"
"certifikata, lahko nato konfigurirate ločeno za podpisne in šifrirne ključe "
"ter (v primeru &smime;) za potrdila za končne uporabnike, vmesna "
"<acronym>CA</acronym> potrdila in potrdila overiterja."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: configure.docbook:2643
#, no-c-format
msgid "GnuPG Settings ..."
msgstr "GnuPG nastavitve ..."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on this button to open an extensive dialog which configures the "
"interactions between &kmail; and &gpg;, the Gnu Privacy Guard program. &gpg; "
"is too complex to document here. For details you should refer to <ulink url="
"\"https://www.gnupg.org/docs.html#guides\">The &GNU; Privacy Handbook</"
"ulink>. Unless you're an encryption expert, you probably ought to accept the "
"default settings here."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na ta gumb odprete obsežno pogovorno okno, ki nastavlja interakcije "
"med &kmail; in &gpg;, programom Gnu Privacy Guard. &gpg; je preveč zapleten, "
"da bi ga tukaj dokumentirali. Podrobnosti so na voljo v <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.gnupg.org/docs.html#guides\">Priročniku o zasebnosti</ulink>. Če niste "
"strokovnjak za šifriranje, bi verjetno morali sprejeti privzete nastavitve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Re-Enable All &quot;Don&apos;t Ask Again&quot; Warnings"
msgstr "Ponovno omogočite vsa &quot;Ne vprašajte še enkrat&quot; opozorila"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the main warnings described above, there are many warning and "
"informational messages, each containing an option not to show them again. If "
"you would like to re-enable these messages after suppressing them, you can "
"achieve that by pressing this button."
msgstr ""
"Poleg glavnih opozoril, opisanih zgoraj, je na voljo še veliko opozorilnih "
"in informativnih sporočil, ki vsebujejo možnost, da se ne prikažejo več. Če "
"želite ta sporočila po ukinitvi ponovno omogočiti, lahko to storite s "
"pritiskom na ta gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will re-enable <emphasis>all</emphasis> such warnings for &kmail;. It "
"does not make much sense to allow more fine-grained selection of which "
"warnings to show since you can just check the option to suppress them again "
"the next time they appear."
msgstr ""
"To bo ponovno omogočilo <emphasis>vsa</emphasis> takšna opozorila za "
"&kmail;. Ni smiselno omogočiti natančnejše izbire opozoril, ki naj se "
"prikažejo, saj lahko ob naslednjem prikazu opozoril preprosto potrdite "
"možnost, da jih ponovno odpravite."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:2688
#, no-c-format
msgid "&smime; Validation"
msgstr "&smime; potrjevanje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:2690
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Security &smime; Validation</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Varnost za &smime; potrjevanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:2696
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Security &smime; Validation</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Varnost za &smime; potrjevanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2699
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Security (&smime; Validation) Tab"
msgstr "Zvihek varnost (za &smime; potrjevanje)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab contains selected entries from &gpgsm;'s <ulink url=\"https://linux."
"die.net/man/1/gpgsm\">dynamic back end configuration dialog</ulink>. Please "
"refer to the &gpgsm; manual for a more detailed description of these options."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek vsebuje izbrane vnose iz <ulink url=\"https://linux.die.net/man/1/"
"gpgsm\">dinamičnega pogovornega okna za konfiguracijo zaledja</ulink>. Za "
"podrobnejši opis teh možnosti glejte priročnik &gpgsm;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Validate certificates using CRLs"
msgstr "Potrdi veljavnost potrdil z uporabo seznamov preklicanih potrdil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &smime; certificates are validated using Certificate Revocation "
"Lists (<acronym>CRLs</acronym>). This is the default configuration option."
msgstr ""
"Če je možnost označena, se potrdila &smime; potrdijo z uporabo seznamov "
"preklicanih potrdil (<acronym>CRL</acronym>). To je privzeta možnost "
"konfiguracije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2729
#, no-c-format
msgid "Validate certificates online (OCSP)"
msgstr "Potrdi veljavnost potrdil preko spleta (OCSP)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, &smime; certificates are validated using the "
"Online Certificates Status Protocol (<acronym>OCSP</acronym>)."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost izbrana, se potrdila &smime; potrdijo z uporabo protokola "
"za stanje spletnih potrdil (<acronym>OCSP</acronym>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2742
#, no-c-format
msgid "OCSP responder &URL;:"
msgstr "OCSP odzivnika &URL;:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the address of the server for online validation of certificates. This "
"&URL; usually starts with <emphasis>https://</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite naslov strežnika za spletno potrjevanje potrdil. Ta &URL; se "
"običajno začne z <emphasis>https://</emphasis>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2754
#, no-c-format
msgid "OCSP responder signature"
msgstr "Podpis odzivnika OSCP"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2757
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select or change and enter the &smime; key to use."
msgstr "Izberite ali spremenite in vnesite tipko &smime; za uporabo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2765
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore service &URL; of certificates"
msgstr "Ignoriranje storitve &URL; potrdil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2768
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this option to skip online validation using the OCSP. This option "
"requires <emphasis>dirmngr &gt;= 0.9.0</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Označite to možnost, če želite preskočiti spletno preverjanje z uporabo "
"OCSP. Ta možnost zahteva <emphasis>dirmngr &gt;= 0.9.0</emphasis>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2777
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not check certificate policies"
msgstr "Ne preveri pravilnikov za potrdila"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, <guilabel>GnuPG</guilabel> uses the file <filename>~/.gnupg/"
"policies.txt</filename> to check if a certificate policy is allowed. If this "
"option is selected, such policies are not checked."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto <guilabel>GnuPG</guilabel> uporabi datoteko <filename>~/.gnupg/"
"policies.txt</filename> za preverjanje, ali je politika potrdil dovoljena. "
"Če je ta možnost izbrana, se takšne politike ne preverijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2791
#, no-c-format
msgid "Never consult a CRLs"
msgstr ""
"Nikoli ne potrdi veljavnosti potrdil z uporabo seznamov preklicanih potrdil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, Certificate Revocation Lists are never used to "
"validate &smime; certificates."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost odkljukana, veljavnost potrdil &smime; nikoli ni preverjena "
"z uporabo seznamov preklicanih potrdil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2803
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fetch missing issuer certificates"
msgstr "Pridobi manjkajoča potrdila izdajateljev"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2806
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this option if you want the missing issuer certificates to be fetched "
"when necessary. This applies to both validation methods, <acronym>CRLs</"
"acronym> and <acronym>OCSP</acronym>."
msgstr ""
"Označite to možnost, če želite, da se manjkajoča potrdila izdajateljev "
"pridobijo po potrebi. To velja za oba načina potrjevanja, <acronym>CRL</"
"acronym> in <acronym>OCSP</acronym>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2816
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not perform any &HTTP; requests"
msgstr "Ne izvajajte nobenih &HTTP; zahtevkov"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2819
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entirely disables the use of &HTTP; for &smime;."
msgstr "Popolnoma onemogoči uporabo &HTTP; za &smime;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2827
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore &HTTP; CRL Distribution Point of certificates"
msgstr "Prezri &HTTP; CRL Distribucijsko točko potrdil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When looking for the location of a CRL, the <quote>to-be-tested</quote> "
"certificate usually contains what are known as CRL Distribution Point "
"(<acronym>DP</acronym>) entries, which are &URL;s describing the way to "
"access the &URL;. The first found <acronym>DP</acronym> entry is used. With "
"this option all entries using the &HTTP; scheme are ignored when looking for "
"a suitable <acronym>DP</acronym>."
msgstr ""
"Pri iskanju lokacije seznama CRL potrdilo <quote>za testiranje</quote> "
"običajno vsebuje tako imenovane vnose CRL Distribution Point (<acronym>DP</"
"acronym>), ki so vnosi &URL;-jev, ki opisujejo način dostopa do &URL;-ja. "
"Uporabi se prvi najden vnos <acronym>DP</acronym>. S to možnostjo se pri "
"iskanju ustreznega <acronym>DP</acronym> ne upoštevajo vsi vnosi, ki "
"uporabljajo shemo &HTTP;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2846
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use system &HTTP; proxy"
msgstr "Uporabljaj sistemski &HTTP; posredniški strežnik"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the value of the &HTTP; proxy shown on the right "
"(which comes from the environment variable <varname>http_proxy</varname>) "
"will be used for any &HTTP; request."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost izbrana, se bo za vsako zahtevo &HTTP; uporabila vrednost "
"posrednika &HTTP;, prikazana na desni strani (ki izhaja iz spremenljivke "
"okolja <varname>http_proxy</varname>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2860
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use this proxy for &HTTP; requests"
msgstr "Uporabljaj ta posredniški strežnik za zahteve &HTTP;"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2863
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the location of your &HTTP; Proxy here, which will be used for all "
"&HTTP; requests relating to &smime;. The syntax is <quote>host:port</quote>, "
"for example, <emphasis>myproxy.nowhere.com:3128</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj vnesite lokacijo svojega posredniškega strežnika &HTTP;, ki se bo "
"uporabljal za vse zahteve &HTTP; v zvezi z &smime;. Sintaksa je "
"<quote>gostitelj:vrata</quote>, na primer <emphasis>myproxy.nowhere."
"com:3128</emphasis>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2875
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not perform any LDAP requests"
msgstr "Ne izvedi nobenih zahtev LDAP"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2878
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entirely disables the use of LDAP for &smime;."
msgstr "Popolnoma onemogoči uporabo protokola LDAP za &smime;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2886
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore LDAP CRL Distribution Point of certificates"
msgstr "Ignoriranje distribucijske točke potrdil LDAP CRL"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When looking for the location of a <acronym>CRL</acronym>, the <quote>to-be-"
"tested</quote> certificate usually contains what are known as CRL "
"Distribution Point (<acronym>DP</acronym>) entries, which are &URL;s "
"describing the way to access the &URL;. The first found <acronym>DP</"
"acronym> entry is used. With this option all entries using the "
"<acronym>LDAP</acronym> scheme are ignored when looking for a suitable "
"<acronym>DP</acronym>."
msgstr ""
"Pri iskanju lokacije <acronym>CRL</acronym> potrdilo <quote>za testiranje</"
"quote> običajno vsebuje tako imenovane vnose CRL Distribution Point "
"(<acronym>DP</acronym>), ki so &URL;-ji, ki opisujejo način dostopa do &URL;"
"ja. Uporabi se prvi najden vnos <acronym>DP</acronym>. S to možnostjo se pri "
"iskanju ustreznega <acronym>DP</acronym> ne upoštevajo vsi vnosi, ki "
"uporabljajo shemo <acronym>LDAP</acronym>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2905
#, no-c-format
msgid "Primary host for LDAP requests"
msgstr "Glaven gostitelj za zahteve LDAP"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering a <acronym>LDAP</acronym> server here will make all <acronym>LDAP</"
"acronym> requests go to that server first. More precisely, this setting "
"overrides any specified host and port part in a <acronym>LDAP</acronym> "
"&URL; and will also be used if host and port have been omitted from the "
"&URL;. Other <acronym>LDAP</acronym> servers will be used only if the "
"connection to the <emphasis>proxy</emphasis> failed. The syntax is "
"<acronym>HOST</acronym> or <acronym>HOST:PORT</acronym>. If <acronym>PORT</"
"acronym> is omitted, <quote>port 389</quote> (standard <acronym>LDAP</"
"acronym> port) is used."
msgstr ""
"Če tukaj vnesete strežnik <acronym>LDAP</acronym>, bodo vse zahteve "
"<acronym>LDAP</acronym> najprej naslovljene na ta strežnik. Natančneje, ta "
"nastavitev prevlada nad vsemi navedenimi deli gostitelja in vrat v "
"<acronym>LDAP</acronym> &URL; in bo uporabljena tudi, če sta gostitelj in "
"vrata v &URL; izpuščena. Drugi strežniki <acronym>LDAP</acronym> bodo "
"uporabljeni le, če povezava s strežnikom <emphasis>posredniški strežnik</"
"emphasis> ni uspela. Sintaksa je <acronym>GOSTITELJ</acronym> ali "
"<acronym>GOSTITELJ:VRATA</acronym>. Če <acronym>VRATA</acronym> izpustite, "
"se uporabijo <quote>vrata 389</quote> (standardna <acronym>LDAP</acronym> "
"vrata)."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:2931
#, no-c-format
msgid "Misc Page"
msgstr "Stran razno"

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:2934
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Mape"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:2936
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Miscellaneous Folders</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Razno za mape</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:2942
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Miscellaneous Folders</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Razno za mape</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2945
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Miscellaneous (Folders) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek razno (za mape)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2964
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exclude important messages from expiry"
msgstr "Od preteka izloči pomembna sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option if important messages should never be deleted "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite to možnost, če želite, da pomembna sporočila ne bodo nikoli "
"izbrisana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:2974
#, no-c-format
msgid "When trying to find unread messages"
msgstr "Ob poskusu iskanja naprebranih sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2976
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option controls what happens if you press one of the shortcuts to go to "
"the next or previous unread message (&eg; <keycap>Space</keycap>). If you "
"ask &kmail; to go to the next unread message although there is no unread "
"message below the currently selected message then the following happens."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost določa, kaj se zgodi, če pritisnete eno od bližnjic za prehod na "
"naslednje ali prejšnje neprebrano sporočilo (&eg; <keycap>Preslednico</"
"keycap>). Če zahtevate, da &kmail; preide na naslednje neprebrano sporočilo, "
"čeprav pod trenutno izbranim sporočilom ni nobenega neprebranega sporočila, "
"se zgodi naslednje."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2984
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Do not Loop</guilabel> is selected then nothing will happen."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <guilabel> Ne kroži </guilabel>, se ne bo zgodilo nič."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2989
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Loop in Current Folder</guilabel> is selected then &kmail; will "
"search from the beginning of the current folder for an unread message. If "
"none is found then nothing happens."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Kroži po trenutni mapi</guilabel>, bo "
"&kmail; iskal neprebrano sporočilo od začetka trenutne mape. Če ne najde "
"nobenega, se ne zgodi nič."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:2996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Loop in All Folders</guilabel> is selected then &kmail; will "
"first search in the current folder for another unread message. If none is "
"found then &kmail; will search the next folder containing unread messages."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Kroži po vseh mapah</guilabel>, bo &kmail; "
"najprej poiskal drugo neprebrano sporočilo v trenutni mapi. Če ne najde "
"nobenega, bo &kmail; poiskal naslednjo mapo z neprebranimi sporočili."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3008
#, no-c-format
msgid "When entering a folder"
msgstr "Ob vstopu v mapo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3010
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option controls what happens when you open a folder."
msgstr "Ta možnost določa, kaj se zgodi, ko odprete neko mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Jump to First Unread Message</guilabel> is selected, &kmail; "
"will select the first message it finds that is marked as unread."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Skoči na prvo neprebrano sporočilo</"
"guilabel>, bo &kmail; izbral prvo sporočilo, ki je označeno kot neprebrano."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3021
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Jump to Last Selected Message</guilabel> is selected, &kmail; "
"will select the message that had been selected when the folder was most "
"recently open."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Skoči na zadnje izbrano sporočilo</"
"guilabel>, bo &kmail; izbral sporočilo, ki je bilo izbrano, ko je bila mapa "
"nazadnje odprta."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Jump to Newest Message</guilabel> is selected, &kmail; will "
"select the newest message."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Skoči na najnovejše sporočilo</guilabel>, bo "
"&kmail; izbral najnovejše sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Jump to Oldest Message</guilabel> is selected, &kmail; will "
"select the oldest message."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Skoči na najstarejše sporočilo</guilabel>, "
"bo &kmail; izbral najstarejše sporočilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3045
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark selected message as read after..."
msgstr "Označi izbrano sporočilo kot preberi kasneje..."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select a <guilabel>new</guilabel> or <guilabel>unread</guilabel> "
"message, &kmail; will change the message's status to <guilabel>read</"
"guilabel> after this many seconds. If you disable this option, messages will "
"retain their <guilabel>new</guilabel> or <guilabel>unread</guilabel> status "
"until you adjust it manually (via the <guilabel>Folder</guilabel> menu)."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete <guilabel>novo</guilabel> ali <guilabel>neprebrano</guilabel> "
"sporočilo, bo &kmail; po tem številu sekund spremenil status sporočila v "
"<guilabel>prebrano</guilabel>. Če to možnost onemogočite, bodo sporočila "
"ohranila svoj status <guilabel>novo</guilabel> ali <guilabel>neprebrano</"
"guilabel>, dokler ga ne nastavite ročno (prek menija <guilabel>Mapa</"
"guilabel>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3059
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ask for action after dragging messages to another folder"
msgstr "Po vlečenju sporočil v drugo mapo vprašaj po dejanju"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3061
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you drag a message to a different folder, a small popup will ask you if "
"you want to move or copy the message. If you disable this option, the "
"message will be moved immediately, without a popup."
msgstr ""
"Ko povlečete sporočilo v drugo mapo, vas majhno pojavno okno vpraša, ali "
"želite sporočilo premakniti ali kopirati. Če to možnost onemogočite, bo "
"sporočilo premaknjeno takoj, brez pojavnega okna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3078
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open this folder on startup"
msgstr "Ob zagonu odpri to mapo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3080
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can set the folder that should be selected when you start &kmail;. "
"If you use only &IMAP; folders then you might want to set this to your "
"&IMAP; inbox folder. If you do that, you can collapse the local folders in "
"the folder list, and they will stay collapsed when &kmail; starts."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko nastavite mapo, ki naj bo izbrana, ko zaženete &kmail;. Če "
"uporabljate samo mape &IMAP;, boste morda želeli to nastaviti na mapo &IMAP; "
"prejeto. Če to storite, lahko lokalne mape na seznamu map zložite in tako "
"ostanejo zložene, ko se zažene program &kmail;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Empty the local trash folder on program exit"
msgstr "Ob izhodu izprazni krajevno mapo s smetmi"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The trash folder is cleared of messages when you quit &kmail; if this option "
"is selected."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaključite program &kmail;, se iz mape za smeti odstranijo sporočila; če "
"je ta možnost izbrana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow deleting messages without confirmation"
msgstr "Dovoli brisanje sporočil brez potrditve"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail;'s default behavior is to ask for confirmation when deleting a "
"message. Select this option if you wish to skip that verification step. "
"(Note that the <guilabel>Delete</guilabel> function is not accessible from "
"&kmail;'s menus. But you can add a <guibutton>Delete</guibutton> button to "
"the toolbar via the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"dialog.)"
msgstr ""
"&kmail;-ovo privzeto obnašanje je, da pri brisanju sporočil zahteva "
"potrditev. To možnost izberite, če želite preskočiti ta korak preverjanja. "
"(Upoštevajte, da funkcija <guilabel>Izbriši</guilabel> ni dostopna v menijih "
"storitve &kmail;. Vendar lahko gumb <guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton> dodate v "
"orodno vrstico prek pogovornega okna <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi orodne vrstice...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)"

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:3118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invitations"
msgstr "Povabila"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:3120
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Miscellaneous Invitation</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Razno za povabila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:3126
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Miscellaneous Invitation</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Razno za povabila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3129
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Miscellaneous (Invitation) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek razno (za povabila)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mangle From:/To: headers in replies to invitations"
msgstr "Pri odzivu na povabila spremeni vrstice Od:/Za: v glavi sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option to make <application>&Microsoft; Outlook</application> "
"understand your reply to an invitation."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite to možnost, da <application>&Microsoft; Outlook</application> "
"razume vaš odgovor na vabilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send invitations in the mail body"
msgstr "Pošlji povabila v telesu sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invitations are usually sent as attachments to a message. When this option "
"is enabled, invitations are sent in the body of the message. This is "
"necessary when sending invitations and replies to <application>&Microsoft; "
"Outlook</application>."
msgstr ""
"Vabila so običajno poslana kot priponke k sporočilu. Če je ta možnost "
"omogočena, so vabila poslana v telesu sporočila. To je potrebno pri "
"pošiljanju vabil in odgovorov v <application>&Microsoft; Outlook</"
"application>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exchange compatible invitations naming"
msgstr "Poimenovanje vabil, združljivih s programom Exchange"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>&Microsoft; Outlook</application>, when used in combination "
"with a &Microsoft; Exchange server, has a problem understanding standards-"
"compliant groupware e-mail. Enable this option to send groupware invitations "
"in a format that &Microsoft; Exchange can decipher. The invitation will be "
"sent as an attachment named <filename>ical.ics</filename>."
msgstr ""
"<application>&Microsoft; Outlook</application>, ki se uporablja v "
"kombinaciji s strežnikom &Microsoft; Exchange, ima težave z razumevanjem e-"
"pošte skupinske programske opreme, skladne s standardi. Omogočite to "
"možnost, če želite vabila za skupinsko programsko opremo pošiljati v obliki, "
"ki jo lahko &Microsoft; Exchange dešifrira. Vabilo bo poslano kot priponka z "
"imenom  <filename>ical.ics</filename>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete invitation emails after the reply to them has been sent"
msgstr ""
"Brisanje e-poštnih sporočil s povabili po tem, ko je bil poslan odgovor nanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this option is checked, invitations that have been replied to will be "
"moved to the Trash folder as soon as the reply has been sent."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bodo vabila, na katera ste odgovorili, takoj po "
"poslanem odgovoru premaknjena v mapo Koš."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:3210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing"
msgstr "Tiskanje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:3212
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Miscellaneous Printing</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Razno za tiskanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:3218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Miscellaneous Printing</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Razno za tiskanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3221
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Miscellaneous (Printing) Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek razno za tiskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog helps you fine tune the way the <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> function operates."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno vam pomaga natančno nastaviti način delovanja funkcije "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Natisni</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print only selected text"
msgstr "Natisni samo izbrano besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option to allow printing of only the selected portion of a "
"message. The default value disables this feature, so the entire message is "
"printed by default."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite to možnost, če želite omogočiti tiskanje samo izbranega dela "
"sporočila. Privzeta vrednost to funkcijo onemogoča, zato se privzeto natisne "
"celotno sporočilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Respect expand/collapse quote marks settings"
msgstr "Spoštovanje nastavitev za razširjanje/zlaganje navedkov"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is intended to interact with the <guilabel>Show expand/collapse "
"quote marks</guilabel> feature of the <link linkend=\"configure-appearance-"
"general\">Appearance/General</link> tab, but it is not currently functioning "
"correctly. In other words, there's a bug."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je namenjena interakciji s funkcijo <guilabel>Pokaži oznake za "
"zlaganje/razširjanje navedkov</guilabel> v zavihku <link linkend=\"configure-"
"appearance-general\">Zgled/splošno</link>, vendar trenutno ne deluje "
"pravilno. Z drugimi besedami, gre za napako."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print background color and images"
msgstr "Natisni barvo ozadja in slike"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like the preceding option, there is a bug here, so &kmail; always prints "
"images, no matter how this option flag is set."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot pri prejšnji možnosti je tudi tu prisotna napaka, zato &kmail; "
"vedno natisne slike, ne glede na to, kako je ta možnost nastavljena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always show encryption/signature details"
msgstr "Vedno pokaži podrobnosti o šifriranju/podpisu"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option to make &kmail; print encryption details for encrypted "
"and/or digitally signed messages."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite to možnost, če želite, da &kmail; natisne podatke o šifriranju za "
"šifrirana in/ali digitalno podpisana sporočila."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:3282
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins Page"
msgstr "Stran za vtičnike"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; contains a large number of special functions that may or may not be "
"useful for particular users. You may select one or more of these special "
"functions by choosing it / them on the \"plugins\" configuration page. Or, "
"if you don't want or need a particular function, you can conserve time and "
"storage space by deselecting the associated plugin module."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; vsebuje veliko število posebnih funkcij, ki so lahko za določene "
"uporabnike koristne ali ne. Eno ali več teh posebnih funkcij lahko izberete "
"tako, da jih izberete na strani za nastvaljanje \"vtičnikov\". Če določene "
"funkcije ne želite ali ne potrebujete, lahko prihranite čas in prostor za "
"shranjevanje tako, da odstranite izbiro povezanega modula vtičnika."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On many Linux distributions, most of these plugins are not included in the "
"basic &kmail; package. To get full plugin functionality, be sure to install "
"the package named \"kdepim-addons\" (or something similar)."
msgstr ""
"V številnih distribucijah Linuxa večina teh vtičnikov ni vključena v osnovni "
"paket &kmail;. Če želite pridobiti polno funkcionalnost vtičnika, obvezno "
"namestite paket z imenom \"kdepim-addons\" (ali kaj podobnega)."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can get a rough idea of what a particular plugin does by simply "
"highlighting the name of the plugin on the &kmail; configuration page. A "
"brief description of that plugin's function will then appear on the right "
"hand side of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Približno predstavo o tem, kaj posamezen vtičnik počne, lahko dobite tako, "
"da preprosto označite ime vtičnika na strani z nastavitvami &kmail;. Na "
"desni strani pogovornega okna se prikaže kratek opis funkcije tega vtičnika."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The various plugins currently available in &kmail; (2021) are listed below. "
"Note that the set of \"default\" plugins is based on the openSUSE version of "
"&kmail; (5.14.2) used as a reference for this edition of the documentation. "
"The actual defaults on your system may be different; they're distro "
"dependent."
msgstr ""
"Različni vtičniki, ki so trenutno na voljo v &kmail; (2021), so navedeni "
"spodaj. Upoštevajte, da nabor \"privzetih\" vtičnikov temelji na različici "
"&kmail;-a v sistemu openSUSE (5.14.2), ki je bila uporabljena kot referenca "
"za to izdajo dokumentacije. Dejanske privzete nastavitve v vašem sistemu so "
"lahko drugačne; odvisne so od distribucije."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because new functionality is added from time to time, this list may grow "
"longer as time passes. There are two general rules governing plugin "
"structure you can count on even if the particular plugin you are confronting "
"is not listed below."
msgstr ""
"Ker občasno dodajamo nove funkcije, se lahko seznam sčasoma podaljša. "
"Obstajata dve splošni pravili o strukturi vtičnikov, na kateri se lahko "
"zanesete, tudi če določen vtičnik, s katerim se soočate, ni naveden spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"1. If the plugin has configurable variables, you can open the configuration "
"dialog for that plugin by clicking the <guibutton>&nbsp;<inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>&nbsp;</guibutton> button appearing next to "
"the plugin's name."
msgstr ""
"1. Če ima vtičnik nastavljive spremenljivke, lahko pogovorno okno za "
"konfiguracijo tega vtičnika odprete tako, da kliknete <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configurebutton.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>&nbsp;</guibutton>, ki se "
"pojavi poleg imena vtičnika."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"2. Whenever a plugin is selected or deselected, &kmail; must be restarted "
"before the desired change(s) can take effect."
msgstr ""
"2. Ko izberete ali odstranite izbiro vtičnika, je treba znova zagnati "
"program &kmail;, da želene spremembe začnejo učinkovati."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:3332
#, no-c-format
msgid "Akonadi and Check Before Send"
msgstr "Akonadi in preveri pred pošiljanjem"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:3334
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Plugins Picture No. One</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Slika vtičnikov št. ena</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:3340
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Plugins Picture No. One</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Slika vtičnikov št. ena</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3343
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins: Akonadi &amp; Check Before Send"
msgstr "Vtičniki: Akonadi &amp; Preveri pred pošiljanjem"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Mail Agent"
msgstr "Posrednik za arhiviranje pošte"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable automatic archiving. See the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_archivemail_agent\">Archive Mail Agent</ulink> documentation for "
"detailed information. You may also wish to read the <link linkend=\"archiving"
"\">Archiving</link> section of this handbook. This plugin is enabled by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti samodejno arhiviranje. Za podrobne "
"informacije glejte <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_archivemail_agent\">Posrednik "
"za arhiviranje pošte</ulink> dokumentacijo. Morda boste želeli prebrati tudi "
"<link linkend=\"archiving\">Razdelek o arhiviranju</link> v tem priročniku. "
"Ta vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Followup Reminder Agent"
msgstr "Posrednik za opombe spremljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable followup reminders. See the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_followupreminder_agent\">Followup Reminder Agent</ulink> "
"documentation for additional information. This plugin is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite omogočiti nadaljnje opomnike. Za dodatne "
"informacije glejte dokumentacijo <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_followupreminder_agent\">Posrednik za opombe spremljanja </ulink>. "
"Ta vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3376
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Email Notifier"
msgstr "Obvestilnik o novi e-pošti"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable new email notifications. You may tailor the "
"fields to be displayed in the \"standard\" notification message. You may "
"also select audio signals (spoken text, pre-recorded sounds), create log "
"file entries, &etc; This plugin is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite omogočiti nova e-poštna obvestila. "
"Prilagodite lahko polja, ki bodo prikazana v \"standardnem\" sporočilu o "
"obvestilu. Izberete lahko tudi zvočne signale (govorjeno besedilo, vnaprej "
"posnete zvoke), ustvarite vnose v dnevniško datoteko in podobno; Ta vtičnik "
"je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send Later Agent"
msgstr "Posrednik za kasnejše pošiljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable delayed dispatching. See the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_sendlater_agent\">Send Later Agent</ulink> documentation for "
"additional information. This plugin is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti odloženo pošiljanje. Za dodatne "
"informacije glejte dokumentacijo <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_sendlater_agent"
"\">Posrednik za kasnejše pošiljanje</ulink>. Ta vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3399
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unified Mailbox Agent"
msgstr "Enotni poštni posrednik"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to create a set of \"unified\" mailboxes. &kmail; will "
"automatically create three of these, labeled Inbox, Drafts, and Sent. If you "
"have defined both a Local Folders inbox and one or more &IMAP; inbox "
"destinations, &kmail; will display all the various inbox files as one "
"consolidated virtual Inbox folder. You may use the configuration dialog to "
"create additional virtual mailboxes, tailoring each one as you see fit. This "
"plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite ustvariti niz enotnih poštnih predalov. "
"&kmail; bo samodejno ustvaril tri take predale z oznakami Prejeto, Osnutki "
"in Odposlano. Če ste določili mapo prejete pošte v lokalnih mapah in eno ali "
"več destinacij prejete pošte &IMAP;, bo &kmail; prikazal vse različne "
"datoteke prejete pošte kot eno združeno virtualno mapo Prejeto. V pogovornem "
"oknu za konfiguracijo lahko ustvarite dodatne virtualne poštne predale in "
"jih prilagodite po lastni presoji. Ta vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3414
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Add Contacts"
msgstr "Samodejno dodaj stike"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add new addresses to one of your address books "
"whenever you send email to a new contact. Use the configuration dialog to "
"associate address books with identities. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite dodati nove naslove v enega od imenikov, "
"kadar koli pošljete e-pošto novemu stiku. Za povezovanje imenikov z "
"identitetami uporabite nastavitveno pogovorno okno. Ta vtičnik je privzeto "
"onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3426
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check Before Send"
msgstr "Preveri pred pošiljanjem"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to apply a few rules before actually sending a message. "
"This plugin is enabled by default, and will automatically notify you when "
"you are trying to send more than one copy of the message to the same person."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite uporabiti nekaj pravil, preden dejansko "
"pošljete sporočilo. Ta vtičnik je privzeto omogočen in vas bo samodejno "
"obvestil, če poskušate isti osebi poslati več kot eno kopijo sporočila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3438
#, no-c-format
msgid "Confirm Address"
msgstr "Potrdi naslov"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable address screening on outgoing messages. Use the "
"configuration dialog to define a white list and/or a black list for each "
"defined identity. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti pregledovanje naslovov v odhodnih "
"sporočilih. V nastavitvenem pogovornem oknu lahko za vsako opredeljeno "
"identiteto določite beli in/ali črni seznam. Ta vtičnik je privzeto "
"onemogočen."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:3453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Composer / Editor"
msgstr "Skladatelj / Urejevalnik"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:3455
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Plugins Picture No. Two</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Slika vtičnikov št. dve</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:3461
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Plugins Picture No. Two</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Slika vtičnikov št. dve</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3464
#, no-c-format
msgid "Composer &amp; Editor"
msgstr "Skladatelj &amp; Urejevalnik"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open External Composer"
msgstr "Odpri zunanji sestavljalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to force the composer to open an external text editor "
"when it starts up. Use the configuration dialog for this plugin to specify "
"the editor that will be called. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite, da se ob zagonu sestavljavca odpre zunanji "
"urejevalnik besedila. V pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo tega vtičnika lahko "
"določite urejevalnik, ki bo poklican. Ta vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3484
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Autocorrection</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Samodejno popravljanje</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Autocorrect Text &gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> function to "
"the composer. This plugin is disabled by default, and is apparently still "
"under construction."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite skladatelju dodati funkcijo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Samodejno popravi "
"besedilo &gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen "
"in je očitno še vedno v pripravi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3496
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change Case"
msgstr "Spremeni velikost črk"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Change Case &gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> function to the "
"composer. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite v sestavljalnik dodati funkcijo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spremeni Case &gt;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Email"
msgstr "Vstavi e-pošto"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Insert Email...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> function to the "
"composer. This lets you insert a selected email address from an address book "
"into the body of your message with a simple point and click of the &LMB;. "
"This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite v skladatelja dodati funkcijo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Insert Email...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Tako lahko izbrani e-poštni naslov iz imenika "
"vstavite v telo sporočila s preprostim pritiskom in klikom na &LMB;. Ta "
"vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3520
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Non Breaking Space"
msgstr "Vstavi nelomljiv presledek"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Insert Non Breaking Space</guimenuitem></menuchoice> function "
"to the composer. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite skladatelju dodati funkcijo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vstavi nelomljiv "
"presledek</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3531
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Short URL"
msgstr "Vstavi kratek URL"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add a tiny bit of not quite functional code. This "
"plugin is still under construction, and is also disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite dodati majhen del ne povsem funkcionalne "
"kode. Ta vtičnik je še vedno v pripravi in je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3541
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Special Character"
msgstr "Vstavi poseben znak"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Insert Special Character...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> function "
"to the composer. This plugin is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite skladatelju dodati funkcijo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vstavi posebni znak...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Text"
msgstr "Hitro besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Snippets</guimenuitem></menuchoice> feature to the composer. "
"This plugin is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite sestavljavcu dodati funkcijo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izrezki</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Ta vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3563
#, no-c-format
msgid "Share Text"
msgstr "Deli besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Share Mail Text &gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> function to the "
"composer. Four options are offered: Nextcloud, Pastebin, Bluetooth, and "
"Email (opens a second composer window). This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite v skladatelja dodati funkcijo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deliti besedilo pošte "
"&gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Na voljo so štiri možnosti: Nextcloud, "
"Pastebin, Bluetooth in e-pošta (odpre se drugo okno skladatelja). Ta vtičnik "
"je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3575
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom Text"
msgstr "Približaj besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zoom... &gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> function to the "
"composer. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite skladatelju dodati funkcijo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Približanje... &gt;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:3590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grammar Check / Header Styles"
msgstr "Pregled slovnice / Slogi glave"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:3592
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Plugins Picture No. Three</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Slika vtičnikov št. tri</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:3598
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Plugins Picture No. Three</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Slika vtičnikov št. tri</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grammar Checkers &amp; Header Styles"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik slovnice &amp; Slogi glave"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3610
#, no-c-format
msgid "French Grammar Checker"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik francoske slovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Check Grammar (Grammalecte)</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option "
"to the Composer window. This option is special, for the French language only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, da v okno skladatelja dodate možnost "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preveri slovnico "
"(Grammalecte)</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta možnost je posebna, samo za "
"francoski jezik."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grammar Checker (Language Tool)"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik slovnice (jezikovno orodje)"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Check Grammar (Language Tool)</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option "
"to the Composer window. This is a multi-purpose tool, with support for "
"checking grammar in many different languages."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, da v okno Composer dodate možnost "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preveri slovnico "
"(jezikovno orodje)</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To je večnamensko orodje s "
"podporo za preverjanje slovnice v več različnih jezikih."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following six plugins permit you to decide which header styles can be "
"selected from the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu. See <link linkend=\"the-"
"preview-pane-headers\">the description of various header views</link> in the "
"\"Using &kmail;\" chapter for more information."
msgstr ""
"Naslednjih šest vtičnikov vam omogoča, da določite, katere sloge glave lahko "
"izberete v meniju <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu>. Za več informacij glejte <link "
"linkend=\"the-preview-pane-headers\">opis različnih prikazov glave</link> v "
"poglavju \"Uporaba &kmail;-a\"."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brief Header Style"
msgstr "Slog s kratkimi glavami"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3647
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable the display of \"Brief\" headers. This plugin "
"is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti prikaz sloga s kratkimi glavami. Ta "
"vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3655
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Grantlee Header Style"
msgstr "Privzet slog z glavami Grantlee"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable the display of \"KMail 5.2\" headers. This "
"plugin is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite omogočiti prikaz glav \"KMail 5.2\". Ta "
"vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3665
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fancy Header Style"
msgstr "Slog z razkošnimi glavami"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable the display of \"Fancy\" headers. This plugin "
"is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti razkošni prikaz glave. Ta vtičnik "
"je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3675
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grantlee Header Style"
msgstr "Slog z glavami Grantlee"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable the display of \"Cute\" headers. This plugin is "
"enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti srčkan prikaz glave. Ta vtičnik je "
"privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3685
#, no-c-format
msgid "Long Header Style"
msgstr "Slog z dolgimi glavami"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable the display of \"Long\" headers. This plugin is "
"disabled by default. (Long headers are similar to standard headers, but will "
"display some less common header information, like \"Reply-to\", when such "
"headers are present.)"
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti prikaz dolgih glav. Ta vtičnik je "
"privzeto onemogočen. (Dolge glave so podobne standardnim glavam, vendar bodo "
"prikazane nekatere manj običajne informacije v glavi, kot je \"Odgovor-na\", "
"če so takšne glave prisotne.)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3697
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standards Header Style"
msgstr "Slog z običajnimi glavami"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable the display of \"Standard\" headers. This "
"plugin is disabled by default. (Standard headers are the same as Fancy "
"headers, but without the shaded background.)"
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti običajen prikaz glave. Ta vtičnik "
"je privzeto onemogočen. (Običajne glave so enake razkošnim glavam, vendar "
"brez senčenega ozadja.)"

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:3712
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Viewer / Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik sporočil / Razno"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:3714
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Plugins Picture No. Four</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Slika vtičnikov št. štiri</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:3720
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Plugins Picture No. Four</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Slika vtičnikov št. štiri</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3723
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Viewer &amp; Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik sporočil &amp; Razno"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3729
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next six plugins all provide special functions that can only be invoked "
"with a toolbar button. Use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Configure Toolbars... </guimenuitem> </menuchoice> dialog to add or remove "
"the toolbar buttons associated with these functions after you select or "
"disable one of these plugins."
msgstr ""
"Naslednjih šest vtičnikov zagotavlja posebne funkcije, ki jih je mogoče "
"priklicati samo z gumbom v orodni vrstici. Uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Nastavi orodne vrstice</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, da , "
"ko izberete ali izključite enega od teh vtičnikov, dodate ali odstranite "
"gumbe orodne vrstice, povezane s temi funkcijami."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3741
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create Event"
msgstr "Ustvari dogodek"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to permit the creation of a calendar event while viewing "
"a &kmail; message. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite omogočiti ustvarjanje koledarskega dogodka "
"med pregledovanjem sporočila &kmail;. Ta vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3751
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create Note"
msgstr "Ustvari opombo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to permit the creation of a &kontact; note while viewing "
"a &kmail; message. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite omogočiti ustvarjanje opombe med "
"pregledovanjem sporočila &kmail;. Ta vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3761
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create Todo"
msgstr "Ustvari opravilo"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to permit the creation of a todo item in &korganizer; "
"while viewing a &kmail; message. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite med pregledovanjem sporočila &kmail; dovoliti "
"ustvarjanje opravila v programu &korganizer;. Ta vtičnik je privzeto "
"onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3771
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand URL"
msgstr "Razširi URL"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable the \"Expand URL\" function. This plugin is "
"enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite omogočiti funkcijo \"Razširi URL\". Ta "
"vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3781
#, no-c-format
msgid "External Script"
msgstr "Zunanji skript"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to permit the invocation of an executable command from "
"the toolbar. Use the associated configuration dialog to select the "
"executable, and to give it a name. The name you choose can later be added to "
"the toolbar as a button, so you may invoke the script at will. This plugin "
"is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti klic izvršljivega ukaza iz orodne "
"vrstice. V povezanem pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo izberite izvršilni "
"program in mu določite ime. Izbrano ime lahko pozneje dodate v orodno "
"vrstico kot gumb, tako da lahko skripto prikličete po želji. Ta vtičnik je "
"privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3794
#, no-c-format
msgid "Translator"
msgstr "Prevajalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3796
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"using-the-translator\">translator function</link> is "
"available in the composer by default. Use this plugin (via the toolbar) to "
"make the translator available in the message preview window. This plugin is "
"enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija <link linkend=\"using-the-translator\">prevajalnik</link> je "
"privzeto na voljo v skladatelju. S tem vtičnikom (v orodni vrstici) "
"omogočite, da je prevajalnik na voljo v oknu za predogled sporočila. Ta "
"vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next four items are not really plugins; they are built-in &kmail; "
"functions. Each one of these can be configured separately, by using the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>&nbsp;</guibutton> button appearing next to the function's "
"name. No restart is needed to make these configuration variables take effect."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji štirje elementi v resnici niso vtičniki; so vgrajene funkcije. "
"Vsako od teh funkcij lahko nastavite ločeno z uporabo gumba <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"configurebutton.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>&nbsp;</guibutton>, ki se "
"pojavi poleg imena funkcije. Za uveljavitev teh nastavitvenih spremenljivk "
"ni potreben ponovni zagon."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3821
#, no-c-format
msgid "DKIM Checker"
msgstr "Program za preverjanje DKIM"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows you to control DomainKeys Identified Mail (DKIM) "
"processing. DKIM is a cryptographic protocol that can assure you a "
"particular message originated from the internet domain it claims to be from. "
"If the sender has set up DKIM properly and DKIM is enabled here, you will "
"see a message \"DKIM valid\", and sometimes the name of the entity that "
"signed the message, in the status bar at the bottom of the message preview "
"window."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko nadzorujete obdelavo pošte z identificiranimi "
"domenskimi ključi (DKIM). DKIM je kriptografski protokol, s katerim lahko "
"zagotovite, da določeno sporočilo izvira iz tiste internetne domene, iz "
"katere trdi, da je. Če je pošiljatelj pravilno nastavil DKIM in je DKIM "
"tukaj omogočen, boste v vrstici stanja na dnu okna za predogled sporočila "
"videli sporočilo \"DKIM velja\" in včasih ime podpisnika."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable this option, be sure to change the default value (\"Nothing\") "
"in the spin box labeled \"Save Record Key\" to some other value. The DKIM "
"Checker does not work correctly if that variable is set to \"Nothing\"."
msgstr ""
"Če to možnost omogočite, spremenite privzeto vrednost (\"Nič\") v vrtilnem "
"polju z oznako \"Shrani ključ zapisa\" v kakšno drugo vrednost. Preverjanje "
"DKIM ne deluje pravilno, če je ta spremenljivka nastavljena na \"Nič\"."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3843
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expire Trash Folder"
msgstr "Potek mape smeti"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3845
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this configuration dialog to set expiry criteria for your trash "
"folder(s). See <link linkend=\"folders-properties-expiry\">\"Folder "
"Properties\"</link> documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"V tem nastavitvenem pogovornem oknu lahko nastavite merila poteka "
"veljavnosti za mape za smeti. Za več informacij glejte <link linkend="
"\"folders-properties-expiry\">\"Lastnosti mape\"</link> dokumentacijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3854
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve mape"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this configuration dialog to set custom folder properties for several "
"different folders at once. You can select the folders to be modified from a "
"tree view of all your folders on the left, and select properties to be set "
"from the General, View, Templates, and Expiry tabs of the <link linkend="
"\"folders-properties-window\">\"Folder Properties\"</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo uporabite za nastavitev lastnosti mape po "
"meri za več različnih map naenkrat. V drevesnem prikazu vseh map lahko na "
"levi strani v zavihkih Splošno, Pogled, Predloge in Iztek veljavnosti v "
"pogovornem oknu <link linkend=\"folders-properties-window\">\"Folder "
"Properties\"</link> izberete mape, ki jih želite spremeniti, in izberete "
"lastnosti, ki jih želite nastaviti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3867
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gravatar"
msgstr "Gravatar"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3869
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this configuration dialog to enable / disable Gravatar (Globally "
"Recognized Avatar) support."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo lahko omogočite ali onemogočite "
"podporo za Gravatar (globalno prepoznani avatar)."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:3881
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "Orodja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configure.docbook:3884
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Plugins Picture No. Five</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Slika vtičnikov št. pet</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configure.docbook:3890
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Plugins Picture No. Five</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Slika vtičnikov št. pet</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3893
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tools &amp; Webengine"
msgstr "Orodja &amp; Spletni pogon"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3902
#, no-c-format
msgid "Antispam"
msgstr "Proti neželeni pošti"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3904
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <link linkend=\"the-anti-spam-wizard\">Anti-"
"Spam Wizard</link> to the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu. This plugin is "
"disabled by default. Note that once you have installed anti-spam software, "
"this plugin may be safely disabled; the plugin is only needed for installing "
"anti-spam software, not for running it."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite dodati <link linkend=\"the-anti-spam-wizard"
"\">Čarovnik za preprečevanje neželene pošte</link> v meni <guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu>. Ta vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen. Upoštevajte, da lahko ta "
"vtičnik po namestitvi programske opreme za preprečevanje neželene pošte "
"varno onemogočite; vtičnik je potreben le za namestitev programske opreme za "
"preprečevanje neželene pošte, ne pa tudi za njeno delovanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3915
#, no-c-format
msgid "Antivirus"
msgstr "Proti virusom"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <link linkend=\"the-anti-virus-wizard\">Anti-"
"Virus Wizard</link> to the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu. This plugin is "
"disabled by default. Note that once you have installed anti-virus software, "
"this plugin may be safely disabled; the plugin is only needed for installing "
"anti-virus software, not for running it."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite dodati <link linkend=\"the-anti-virus-wizard"
"\">Protivirusni čarovnik</link> v meni <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu>. Ta vtičnik "
"je privzeto onemogočen. Upoštevajte, da lahko po namestitvi protivirusne "
"programske opreme ta vtičnik varno onemogočite; vtičnik je potreben le za "
"namestitev protivirusne programske opreme, ne pa tudi za njeno delovanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3928
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expert Plugin"
msgstr "Napredni vtičnik"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Message Structure Ctrl+Alt+D</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"function in the message preview window. This plugin is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite v okno za predogled sporočila dodati funkcijo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži strukturo "
"sporočila Ctrl+Alt+D</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta vtičnik je privzeto "
"omogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3939
#, no-c-format
msgid "Log Activities"
msgstr "Beleži dejanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to enable the Activity Log function, which is disabled by "
"default. This plugin adds a new entry <guilabel>Log Activities</guilabel> to "
"the <guilabel>Tools</guilabel> menu. Primarily for use by program developers "
"-- the default log function does not provide much information (just a time "
"stamp and \"Ready\", for most \"events\")."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izberite, če želite omogočiti funkcijo dnevnika dejavnosti, ki je "
"privzeto onemogočena. Ta vtičnik doda nov vnos <guilabel>Beleži dejanja</"
"guilabel> v meni <guilabel>Orodja</guilabel>. Služi predvsem za uporabo s "
"strani razvijalcev programov - privzeta funkcija dnevnika ne zagotavlja "
"veliko informacij (le časovni žig in \"Pripravljen\" za večino \"dogodkov\")."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3952
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adblock"
msgstr "Adblock"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to add the <ulink url=\"https://adblockplus.org\">Adblock "
"Plus</ulink> filters to &kmail;. If you choose to activate this plugin, be "
"prepared to spend a good deal of time tweaking the configuration file to get "
"the filters you really want. This plugin is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite dodati filtre <ulink url=\"https://"
"adblockplus.org\">Adblock Plus</ulink> v &kmail;. Če se odločite aktivirati "
"ta vtičnik, se pripravite, da boste porabili veliko časa za prilagajanje "
"nastavitvene datoteke, da boste dobili filtre, ki jih resnično želite. Ta "
"vtičnik je privzeto onemogočen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:3964
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do Not Track"
msgstr "Ne sledi mi"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to force &kmail; to send a \"Do Not Track\" request to a "
"remote server when an &HTML; message asks to download remote content. The "
"effect of a \"Do Not Track\" request depends on the policy adopted by the "
"web server receiving the request. Some sites honor it. Others don't."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite, da &kmail;, ko sporočilo &HTML; zahteva "
"prenos oddaljene vsebine, pošlje zahtevo \"Ne sledi mi\" oddaljenemu "
"strežniku. Učinek zahteve \"Ne sledi mi\" je odvisen od pravilnika, ki ga "
"sprejme spletni strežnik, ki prejme zahtevo. Nekatera spletna mesta jo "
"upoštevajo, druga ne."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Advertisers have their eyes everywhere. &HTML;-encoded messages often "
"include a 0x0- or 1x1-pixel \"image\" (aka a \"tracking pixel\") that is "
"actually a tracking &URL; in disguise. When &kmail; fetches image data from "
"a web server, it must utilize the &URL;s embedded in the message; the server "
"can use information embedded in the &URL; to infer that you have opened the "
"message, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Oglaševalci imajo oči povsod. Sporočila, kodirana v jeziku &HTML;, pogosto "
"vključujejo \"sliko\" v velikosti 0x0 ali 1x1 slik. točk (t. i. \"sledilni "
"piksel\"/\"sledilna slikovna točka\"), ki je v resnici prikrit sledilni "
"naslov &URL;. Ko &kmail; pridobiva slikovne podatke iz spletnega strežnika, "
"mora uporabiti &URL;-je, ki so vključeni v sporočilo; strežnik lahko uporabi "
"informacije, vključene v &URL;, da sklepa, da ste odprli sporočilo, &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sending a \"Do Not Track\" request may enhance your privacy slightly. But "
"the only certain way to avoid tracking pixels is never to download remote "
"images encoded in &HTML; messages. This plugin is enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Pošiljanje zahtevka \"Ne sledi mi\" lahko nekoliko izboljša vašo zasebnost. "
"Edini zanesljivi način, da se izognete sledilnim slikovnim pikam, pa je, da "
"nikoli ne prenesete oddaljenih slik, kodiranih v sporočilih &HTML;. Ta "
"vtičnik je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: title
#: configure.docbook:3993
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options without a user interface representation"
msgstr "Možnosti, ki niso predstavljene z uporabniškim vmesnikom"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:3994
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the options presented in the configuration dialog, some options "
"can only be set directly in the &kmail; configuration file or through KIOSK "
"(&eg; Input into &konsole;). These so called <quote>hidden</quote> "
"configuration options cannot be changed via the normal &kmail; Settings "
"dialog; they must be made by modifying the configuration file using a text "
"editor or the <command>kwriteconfig</command> program. The configuration "
"file is to be written in the format of [Section Name] and the following "
"lines are the variables and their settings. If you are manually editing the "
"configuration file you will need to add the [Section Name] before adding "
"variables. The <command>kwriteconfig</command> will add the section for you "
"as long as you use the <userinput>--group</userinput> switch."
msgstr ""
"Poleg možnosti, predstavljenih v pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo, lahko "
"nekatere možnosti nastavite samo neposredno v nastavitveni datoteki &kmail; "
"ali prek sistema KIOSK (&eg; Vnos v &konsole;). Teh tako imenovanih "
"<quote>skritih</quote> nastavitvenih možnosti ni mogoče spremeniti v "
"običajnem pogovornem oknu &kmail; Nastavitve; spremeniti jih je treba s "
"spreminjanjem nastavitvene datoteke z urejevalnikom besedila ali programom "
"<command>kwriteconfig</command>. Nastavitveno datoteko je treba zapisati v "
"obliki [Ime odseka], v naslednjih vrsticah pa so spremenljivke in njihove "
"nastavitve. Če nastavitveno datoteko urejate ročno, morate pred dodajanjem "
"spremenljivk dodati [Ime odseka]. Ukaz <command>kwriteconfig</command> bo "
"dodal razdelek namesto vas, če boste uporabili stikalo <userinput>--group</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4003
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kmail; configuration file is called <filename>kmail2rc</filename> and "
"can be found in your home directory. The location may vary according to your "
"operating system or distribution, but can always be found by running the "
"command <userinput><command>kf5-config --path config --locate kmail2rc</"
"command></userinput>. For the remainder of this section, assume that the "
"configuration file is located in <filename>/path/to/kmail2rc</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitvena datoteka za &kmail; se imenuje <filename>kmail2rc</filename> in "
"jo najdete v domačem imeniku. Lokacija se lahko razlikuje glede na "
"operacijski sistem ali distribucijo, vendar jo lahko vedno najdete z ukazom "
"<userinput><command>kf5-config --path config --locate kmail2rc</command></"
"userinput>. V nadaljevanju tega poglavja predpostavimo, da se nastavitvena "
"datoteka nahaja v datoteki <filename>/path/to/kmail2rc</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4012
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever changing these options, make sure to quit &kmail; first before "
"editing the configuration file. Only restart &kmail; after you have made "
"<emphasis>and saved</emphasis> the changes to the configuration file."
msgstr ""
"Če spreminjate te možnosti, se pred urejanjem nastavitve datoteke najprej "
"prepričajte, da ste zaključili &kmail;. &kmail; ponovno zaženite šele, ko "
"ste opravili <emphasis>in shranili</emphasis> spremembe v nastavitveni "
"datoteki."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:4021
#, no-c-format
msgid "SendMDNsWithEmptySender"
msgstr "SendMDNsWithEmptySender"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Send Message Disposition Notifications with an empty sender string. Some "
"servers might be configured to reject such messages, so if you are "
"experiencing problems sending MDNs, make sure this option is set to false. "
"To enable this feature, add to the <quote>[MDN]</quote> section:"
msgstr ""
"Pošiljanje obvestil o razporeditvi sporočila s praznim nizom pošiljatelja. "
"Nekateri strežniki so morda nastvaljeni tako, da zavračajo takšna sporočila, "
"zato če imate težave s pošiljanjem MDN, preverite, ali je ta možnost "
"nastavljena na false (ne drži). Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo, jo dodajte "
"v razdelek <quote>[MDN]</quote>:"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4028 configure.docbook:4050 configure.docbook:4072
#: configure.docbook:4089 configure.docbook:4107 configure.docbook:4125
#: configure.docbook:4144 configure.docbook:4161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration file:"
msgstr "Nastavitvena datoteka:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configure.docbook:4029
#, no-c-format
msgid "SendMDNsWithEmptySender=true"
msgstr "SendMDNsWithEmptySender=true"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4031
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group MDN --"
"key SendMDNsWithEmptySender true</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group MDN --"
"key SendMDNsWithEmptySender true</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default setting of <quote>false</quote> strictly speaking violates "
"Internet standards, but is set that way for practical reasons, to avoid "
"servers rejecting MDNs that &kmail; generates because they think they are "
"SPAM."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta nastavitev <quote>false</quote> (ne drži) strogo gledano krši "
"internetne standarde, vendar je tako nastavljena iz praktičnih razlogov, da "
"strežniki ne bi zavrnili MDN, ki jih &kmail; generira, ker menijo, da so "
"SPAM."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:4042
#, no-c-format
msgid "CloseDespiteSystemTray"
msgstr "CloseDespiteSystemTray"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4044
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to configure the application to close fully, even if "
"there is a system tray icon configured, which would normally keep the "
"application running. To enable the feature, add to the <quote>[General]</"
"quote> section:"
msgstr ""
"S to možnostjo lahko nastavite, da se aplikacija popolnoma zapre, tudi če je "
"ikona v sistemski vrstici nastavljena, zaradi katere bi aplikacija običajno "
"ostala zagnana. Če želite omogočiti funkcijo, jo dodajte v razdelek "
"<quote>[General]</quote>:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configure.docbook:4051
#, no-c-format
msgid "CloseDespiteSystemTray=true"
msgstr "CloseDespiteSystemTray=true"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group General "
"--key CloseDespiteSystemTray true</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group General "
"--key CloseDespiteSystemTray true</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:4061
#, no-c-format
msgid "disregardUmask"
msgstr "disregardUmask"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In versions prior to 1.9, &kmail; saved all attachments to disk with "
"permissions set to 600 &mdash; only readable or writable by the owner of the "
"file. In response to user feedback, this was made configurable in &kmail; "
"version 1.9, with the defaults changed to honor the umask set on the user "
"account while saving files to disk. To enable this feature, add to the "
"<quote>[General]</quote> section:"
msgstr ""
"V različicah pred 1.9 je &kmail; vse priponke shranil na disk z dovoljenji, "
"nastavljenimi na 600 &mdash; brati ali pisati jih je smel samo lastnik "
"datoteke. Kot odziv na povratne informacije uporabnikov je bilo to mogoče "
"nastaviti v različici 1.9 programa &kmail; privzete nastavitve so bile "
"spremenjene tako, da se med shranjevanjem datotek na disk upošteva umask, "
"nastavljena v uporabniškem računu. Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo, jo "
"dodajte v razdelek <quote>[General]</quote>:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configure.docbook:4073
#, no-c-format
msgid "disregardUmask=true"
msgstr "disregardUmask=true"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4075
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group General "
"--key disregardUmask true</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group General "
"--key disregardUmask true</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:4081
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckOutOfOfficeOnStartup"
msgstr "CheckOutOfOfficeOnStartup"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option enabled, &kmail; will check on every startup if there is an "
"active out-of-office reply configured, and show a warning if this is the "
"case. To disable the feature, add to the <quote>[OutOfOffice]</quote> "
"section:"
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena, bo &kmail; ob vsakem zagonu preveril, ali je "
"nastavljen aktiven odgovor izven pisarne, in v tem primeru prikazal "
"opozorilo. Če želite funkcijo onemogočiti, jo dodajte v razdelek "
"<quote>[OutOfOffice]</quote>:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configure.docbook:4090
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckOutOfOfficeOnStartup=false"
msgstr "CheckOutOfOfficeOnStartup=false"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key CheckOutOfOfficeOnStartup false</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key CheckOutOfOfficeOnStartup false</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:4100
#, no-c-format
msgid "AllowOutOfOfficeSettings"
msgstr "AllowOutOfOfficeSettings"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case you don't want users to be able to upload their own out-of-office "
"scripts to the server you may add to the <quote>[OutOfOffice]</quote> "
"section:"
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite, da bi uporabniki lahko na strežnik naložili svoje lastne "
"skripte, ki niso v pisarni, lahko dodate v razdelek <quote>[OutOfOffice]</"
"quote>:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configure.docbook:4108
#, no-c-format
msgid "AllowOutOfOfficeSettings=false"
msgstr "AllowOutOfOfficeSettings=false"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key AllowOutOfOfficeSettings false</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key AllowOutOfOfficeSettings false</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:4118
#, no-c-format
msgid "AllowOutOfOfficeUploadButNoSettings"
msgstr "AllowOutOfOfficeUploadButNoSettings"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to allow your users to upload their own out-of-office scripts "
"but you do not want them to be able to change the domain to react to and the "
"react-to-spam setting, you may add to the <quote>[OutOfOffice]</quote> "
"section:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabnikom omogočiti, da naložijo svoje skripte zunaj pisarne, "
"vendar ne želite, da bi lahko spremenili domeno, na katero se bodo odzvali, "
"in nastavitev odzivanja na neželeno pošto, lahko v razdelek "
"<quote>[OutOfOffice]</quote> dodate:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configure.docbook:4126
#, no-c-format
msgid "AllowOutOfOfficeUploadButNoSettings=true"
msgstr "AllowOutOfOfficeUploadButNoSettings=true"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key AllowOutOfOfficeUploadButNoSettings true</option></"
"userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key AllowOutOfOfficeUploadButNoSettings true</option></"
"userinput>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:4136
#, no-c-format
msgid "OutOfOfficeDomain"
msgstr "OutOfOfficeDomain"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When editing vacation (out-of-office) scripts, the user may specify a domain "
"to limit the sending of such replies to. Applying defaults to the out-of-"
"office configuration dialog via the corresponding button will restore this "
"domain, in case the user has changed it. To pre-load this setting with a "
"default value, add to the <quote>[OutOfOffice]</quote> section:"
msgstr ""
"Pri urejanju skript napisanih na dopustu (izven pisarne) lahko uporabnik "
"določi domeno, ki ji želi omejiti pošiljanje takih odgovorov. Uporaba "
"privzetih nastavitev v nastavitvenem pogovornem oknu zunaj pisarne z "
"ustreznim gumbom bo obnovila to domeno, če jo je uporabnik spremenil. Če "
"želite vnaprej naložiti to nastavitev s privzeto vrednostjo, jo dodajte v "
"razdelek <quote>[OutOfOffice]</quote>:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configure.docbook:4145
#, no-c-format
msgid "OutOfOfficeDomain=myMailDomain.test"
msgstr "OutOfOfficeDomain=myMailDomain.test"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key OutOfOfficeDomain myMailDomain.test</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key OutOfOfficeDomain myMailDomain.test</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:4155
#, no-c-format
msgid "OutOfOfficeReactToSpam"
msgstr "OutOfOfficeReactToSpam"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, out-of-office replies are not sent to messages marked as SPAM. "
"To override this behavior, add to the [OutOfOffice] section:"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je, da se na sporočila, ki so označena kot SPAM, ne pošiljajo "
"odgovori izven pisarne. Če želite preklicati to vedenje, dodajte v razdelek "
"[OutOfOffice]:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configure.docbook:4162
#, no-c-format
msgid "OutOfOfficeReactToSpam=true"
msgstr "OutOfOfficeReactToSpam=true"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:4164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key OutOfOfficeReactToSpam true</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <userinput><command>kwriteconfig</command> "
"<option>--file <replaceable>/path/to/kmail2rc</replaceable> --group "
"OutOfOffice --key OutOfOfficeReactToSpam true</option></userinput>"

